NK014(pha)002:0: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo he ru ka'i dkyil
NK014(pha)002:1: 'khor bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs bde chen char 'bebs zhes
NK014(pha)002:4: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo he ru ka'i dkyil
NK014(pha)002:5: 'khor bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs bde chen char 'bebs zhes
NK014(pha)002:6: bya ba / dpal ldan bla ma he ru ka dang gnyis su med pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)002:7: don dam 'gyur med bde chen he ru ka /
NK014(pha)002:8: spros bral gdod ma'i dbyings phyug mas 'khyud pa //
NK014(pha)002:9: rdo rje khro bo lnga bcu rtsa brgyad lha //
NK014(pha)002:10: dkyil 'khor 'khor lor bcas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)002:11: he ru ka dpal bde chen mchog gi grong //
NK014(pha)002:12: srid zhi'i mtha' las rnam par grol ba'i gzhir //
NK014(pha)002:13: myur bder bgrod pa'i lam bzang do zla med //
NK014(pha)002:14: rdo rje 'dzin dbang tshogs kyis gshegs pa'i shul //
NK014(pha)002:15: yi ges mtshon min de las gsal 'char ba //
NK014(pha)002:16: gdod ma'i dpa' bo skul byed rdo rje'i dbyangs //
NK014(pha)002:17: bde chen char du 'bebs pa sprin gyi sgrar //
NK014(pha)002:18: len no dngos grub gnas la dbugs 'byin mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:24: sgrub pa po dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir zhugs shing /
NK014(pha)002:25: phyi nang gi dbang thob pa /
NK014(pha)002:26: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig la yang dag par gnas pa'o //
NK014(pha)002:30: rjes kyi rim pa dang gsum las /
NK014(pha)002:32: dang po bya ba'i sngon 'gro ni /
NK014(pha)002:33: dur khrod dang ri bo dben pa la sogs pa
NK014(pha)002:34: bsam gtan dang rjes su mthun pa'i gnas khang mdzes
NK014(pha)002:35: par brgyan / rten dang phyi nang gi mchod gtor
NK014(pha)002:36: sogs mkho ba'i yo byad rnams tshogs par bshams nas
NK014(pha)002:38: tshul phyag sngon du 'gro bas bde ba'i stan la 'dug ste /
NK014(pha)002:39: rol mos byin dbab pa rnams bya'o //
NK014(pha)002:40: gnyis pa rgyud sbyang ba ni /
NK014(pha)002:41: rang gi snying ga'i h+aum gi 'od zer gyis rang
NK014(pha)002:42: bzhin gyi gnas nas bla ma dang gnyis su med
NK014(pha)002:43: pa'i dpal he ru ka la phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i
NK014(pha)002:44: skyabs yul ma tshang ba med pas bskor ba thams
NK014(pha)002:45: cad mdun gyi nam mkhar badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs sad
NK014(pha)002:46: par byas la / bdag dang mkha' mnyam sems can rnams //
NK014(pha)002:47: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK014(pha)002:48: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)002:49: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK014(pha)002:50: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK014(pha)002:51: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:52: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK014(pha)002:53: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK014(pha)002:54: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK014(pha)002:55: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK014(pha)002:56: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK014(pha)002:57: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK014(pha)002:58: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK014(pha)002:59: bde gshegs byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK014(pha)002:60: dag pa gsum gyi lus dbul lo //
NK014(pha)002:61: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK014(pha)002:62: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK014(pha)002:63: zhes lan gsum la sogs pas rgyud dag par byas la /
NK014(pha)002:64: tshogs zhing rnams rang la bsdus te /
NK014(pha)002:65: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs spros bral stong pa nyid kyi ngang la mnyam bzhag bya'o //
NK014(pha)002:66: gsum pa mtshams bcad pa la /
NK014(pha)002:71: 'di ltar gzung ba dang 'dzin pas bsdus pa mtshan
NK014(pha)002:72: ma'i dmigs yul thams cad stong zhing bdag med pa
NK014(pha)002:73: nam mkha' lta bur bsgoms pas tha mal gyi bden
NK014(pha)002:75: stong pa'i ngang las pad nyi la gnas pa'i h+aum las sna tshogs rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan pa /
NK014(pha)002:77: rdo rje'i sa gzhi ra ba d+r+wa ba gur bla re /
NK014(pha)002:78: phyi rol bskal pa'i me dpung rab tu 'bar bas bskor ba'i dbus su /
NK014(pha)002:79: b+h+r+au las 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bcu pa rtse
NK014(pha)002:80: mo rno ba'i dbal dang ldan pa drag tu 'khor
NK014(pha)002:81: zhing / khog pa stong pa chos kyi dbyings dang
NK014(pha)002:82: mnyam pa'i dbus su pad nyi la gnas pa'i h+aum
NK014(pha)002:84: de las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs dam bskul /
NK014(pha)002:85: gcig tu 'dus nas h+aum la zhugs pa las /
NK014(pha)002:86: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka bdag nyid zhe sdang rdo rje sku mdog mthing nag /
NK014(pha)002:87: mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi /
NK014(pha)002:88: g.yas gsum rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che /
NK014(pha)002:89: g.yon gsum dril bu pad+ma ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)002:90: nyi ma 'bum gyi gzi brjid can /
NK014(pha)002:91: gar dgu'i nyams kyis sgeg cing /
NK014(pha)002:92: dur khrod rol pa'i chas kyis brgyan pa /
NK014(pha)002:93: yum kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i skur gyur /
NK014(pha)002:94: de'i thugs ka'i h+aum las ma bcu 'phros pa rtsibs nang rnams su nyi gdan bcur gyur /
NK014(pha)002:95: slar yang thugs ka nas khro bo 'dod pa'i rgyal po spros /
NK014(pha)002:96: phyogs bcu'i bgegs rnams bkug ste nyi gdan rnams kyi
NK014(pha)002:97: steng du myos shing 'gyel stabs su 'khod par bsam
NK014(pha)002:100: gri h+na p+aa ya gri h+na p+aa ya h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:101: +aa na ya hoh b+ha ga w+aan bid+ya r+aa dza h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:112: e ra pa ti ye dzahh+aum bam hoh slar yang rang gi thugs ka nas h+aum yig bcu 'phros /
NK014(pha)002:113: so so'i gdan la 'khod pa las /
NK014(pha)002:114: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum gardza gardza h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:115: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h+aum ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:116: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h+aum da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:117: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:118: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum b+han+d+ha b+han+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:119: badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:120: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa r+aa dzi ta h+aum tish+tha tish+tha h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:121: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum ts+tshin+da ts+tshin+da h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:122: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dza ya h+aum b+hin+da b+hin+da h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:123: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h+aum s+pho ta s+pho ta h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:125: h+aum yig rnams rim pa bzhin h+aum mdzad la sogs pa khro bo bcur gyur te /
NK014(pha)002:126: thams cad kyang sku mdog mthing nag /
NK014(pha)002:127: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa tho ba dang lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)002:128: smad phur bu 'bar ba'i rnam pa can du gyur par bsam zhing /
NK014(pha)002:129: de nas khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba tho ba thogs pa sprul te /
NK014(pha)002:130: g+ha g+ha g+h+aa ta ya g+h+aa ta ya /
NK014(pha)002:132: k+ai la ya k+ai la ya sarba p+aa pam phata /
NK014(pha)002:134: badz+ra k+ai la ya badz+ra d+ha ra a dz+ny+aa pa
NK014(pha)002:135: ya ti sarba big+h+n+aam k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra
NK014(pha)002:138: khro bo rnams phyogs bcu'i bgegs la phur bu'i tshul du btab pas /
NK014(pha)002:139: de rnams kyi lus phug ste g.yo 'gul med par byas nas /
NK014(pha)002:140: slar yang de rnams las sprul pa dang yang sprul
NK014(pha)002:141: mtshon cha sna tshogs dang bcas pa'i 'od zer rnon
NK014(pha)002:142: po 'khrug cing / 'bar ba srung ba'i 'khor los
NK014(pha)002:143: phyogs kun gtams te cis kyang mi shigs par bsam
NK014(pha)002:145: ba'i mtshams gcod gleng gzhi ltar 'byor bar snang yang
NK014(pha)002:146: po 'khrug cing / mo // / gong ma'i phyag len bzhin de ltar byas so //
NK014(pha)002:147: bzhi pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK014(pha)002:149: bla ma rig 'dzin zhi khro rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i
NK014(pha)002:150: tshogs dang bcas pa mngon sum du sad pa'i spyan
NK014(pha)002:151: sngar / sems can thams cad kyi don du mchog
NK014(pha)002:152: gi byang chub tshe 'di nyid kyis mngon du bya
NK014(pha)002:154: tshe rabs thog med nas bsags pa'i mi dge ba'i las rnams la gnong zhing 'gyod /
NK014(pha)002:155: phyin chad srog la babs kyang mi bgyid /
NK014(pha)002:156: sngar byas kyi gnyen por rnal 'byor gyi rim pa la 'jug par bagyi'o snyam pa'i sems brtan pos /
NK014(pha)002:158: ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ni //
NK014(pha)002:159: zla rgyas bzhin du spros pa mi mnga' yang //
NK014(pha)002:160: thugs rje nyi gsal 'od bzhin snyoms mdzad pa //
NK014(pha)002:161: 'dir gshegs bdag la dgongs shing bzhugs su gsol //
NK014(pha)002:162: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo chos kyi sku //
NK014(pha)002:163: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs sku rigs lnga'i gtso //
NK014(pha)002:164: thugs rje thabs mkhas rgya che rol pa'i lha //
NK014(pha)002:165: zhi khro sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)002:166: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:167: kun tu bzang po bla med mchod sprin gyis //
NK014(pha)002:168: mkha' dbyings rnam dag rgya cher yongs bkod de //
NK014(pha)002:169: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rgya mtshos mchod //
NK014(pha)002:170: kun tu bzang mo gsang ba'i b+ha ga la //
NK014(pha)002:171: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus rab 'byams kun //
NK014(pha)002:172: 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang du ro gcig pa //
NK014(pha)002:173: gnyis med byang chub sems kyis mnyes gyur cig /
NK014(pha)002:174: sems kyi rang bzhin chos dbyings nam mkha' che //
NK014(pha)002:175: chos rnams rnam dag ye nas 'od gsal zhing //
NK014(pha)002:176: rnal 'byor nyid dbyings smra bsam las 'das pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:177: mnyam nyid byang chub sems la rtag tu 'dud //
NK014(pha)002:178: kun bzang rdzogs chen ye nas brdal ba la //
NK014(pha)002:179: phyi nang gsang ba bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK014(pha)002:180: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i dbyings //
NK014(pha)002:181: 'byung dang 'byung 'gyur yab yum lhun rdzogs rnams //
NK014(pha)002:182: gsang chen rab dgyes gzugs can bdag nyid ma //
NK014(pha)002:183: mkha' dbyings klong yangs pad+mo 'khyil ba la //
NK014(pha)002:184: gnyis med thig le chen por 'od gsal zhing //
NK014(pha)002:185: ma bcos spros med byang chub snying po'i sku //
NK014(pha)002:186: cir yang snang ba bde chen g.yung drung lha //
NK014(pha)002:188: bdag nyid chen po rigs lnga yab yum dang //
NK014(pha)002:189: byang chub lcam dral khro bo khro mo'i tshogs //
NK014(pha)002:190: rdo rje lha mo tshogs rje tshogs kyi bdag /
NK014(pha)002:191: rigs lnga dpal chen khro rgyal yab yum bcu //
NK014(pha)002:192: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya sgo ma bzhi //
NK014(pha)002:193: ye shes sprul pa'i lha tshogs mang po dang //
NK014(pha)002:194: ma ltar byams shing sring ltar gdung la sogs //
NK014(pha)002:195: legs nyes stangs 'dzin dam tshig rjes gcod ma //
NK014(pha)002:196: phyi nang mkha' 'gro rnal 'byor ma yi tshogs //
NK014(pha)002:197: dpang gyur rdo rje dam can dgongs su gsol //
NK014(pha)002:199: thugs rje gdung 'tshob rig 'dzin bdag cag gis //
NK014(pha)002:200: 'gro ba'i don du byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK014(pha)002:201: bla med go 'phang bgrod par bya ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)002:202: bstan pa rgya mtsho so so'i 'dul khrims dang //
NK014(pha)002:203: sku gsung thugs dang mnyam sbyor sdom pa'i mchog /
NK014(pha)002:204: rdo rje 'da' dka' dam tshig gtan gyi gnyer //
NK014(pha)002:205: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK014(pha)002:206: snga phyir mnos shing gnyer du smras so 'tshal //
NK014(pha)002:207: yun du mi gtong 'da' bar mi bgyid cing //
NK014(pha)002:208: don las gol zhing ldog sems ma mchis kyang //
NK014(pha)002:209: gdod bya long yod snyam pa'i le lo yis //
NK014(pha)002:210: klong du ma gyur rtsal shugs chung ba dang //
NK014(pha)002:211: shes bzhin mi ldan bag med dbang gyur te //
NK014(pha)002:212: sgom la mi brtson bsnyen sgrub g.yel la sogs //
NK014(pha)002:213: tshor dang ma tshor ma rig dbang gis na //
NK014(pha)002:214: ston pa'i bka' dang dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK014(pha)002:215: rnal 'byor gang zhig dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK014(pha)002:216: skad cig tsam yang 'phrad par mi bya zhes //
NK014(pha)002:217: bka' las byung zhing de ltar ma lcogs te //
NK014(pha)002:218: gsang sgo 'chol bas dbye bsal dkas pa dang //
NK014(pha)002:219: mngon shes med pas skyon can ma rtogs te //
NK014(pha)002:220: nyams dang tshogs 'dres nyams pa bskangs pa dang //
NK014(pha)002:221: nyams dang snod min rnams la chos bshad dang //
NK014(pha)002:222: nyams la ma 'dzem nyams pa'i skyon la sogs //
NK014(pha)002:223: nyams dang 'grogs shing nyams pa de dag gi //
NK014(pha)002:224: nyams sgrib skyon gyis gos par gyur to 'tshal //
NK014(pha)002:225: tshe 'di'i rkyen dang yun gyi sgrib gyur rnams //
NK014(pha)002:226: rang gnong 'gyod pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK014(pha)002:227: byams pa'i thugs brtses bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK014(pha)002:228: gnyis med dbyings las mi 'gyur bdag bkod de //
NK014(pha)002:229: dmigs med btang snyoms ngang du bzhugs nas kyang //
NK014(pha)002:230: gnyis med don gyi tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)002:231: don dam dmigs med spros las 'das pas na //
NK014(pha)002:232: rnam rtog gang yang dmigs par mi 'gyur zhing //
NK014(pha)002:233: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam gyi dbang gis na //
NK014(pha)002:234: nongs par mchis na rab nongs bzod par gsol //
NK014(pha)002:235: zhes brjod pas sdig sgrib thams cad byang bar mos
NK014(pha)002:236: nas mnyam pa nyid kyi don la blo bzhag go
NK014(pha)002:237: // lnga pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK014(pha)002:238: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i rgya bcings te /
NK014(pha)002:239: lhag pa'i bsam pa brtan pos //
NK014(pha)002:240: rnal 'byor dbang po ye shes mthar phyin pa //
NK014(pha)002:241: 'gro la phan mdzad thugs rjes dbang sgyur zhing //
NK014(pha)002:242: srid pa gsum gyi gnyen gyur gcig pu pa //
NK014(pha)002:243: lha yi lha khyod bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK014(pha)002:244: bde bar gshegs pa'i sprul pa rgya mtsho dang //
NK014(pha)002:245: rnal 'byor dbang phyug grub pa'i tshogs chen po //
NK014(pha)002:246: lha dang lha min sngags 'chang dam tshig can //
NK014(pha)002:247: kun nas 'dus pa rnams kyang dgongs su gsol //
NK014(pha)002:248: bdag ni rgyal srid mtho ris longs spyod dang //
NK014(pha)002:249: 'dod pa'i yon tan bdag sgrub ma lags te //
NK014(pha)002:250: 'gro la snying brtse kho nas don brtson pa //
NK014(pha)002:251: 'di la kun mkhyen khyod ni dpang du gsol //
NK014(pha)002:252: mgon po ye shes sgrib pa mi mnga' bas //
NK014(pha)002:253: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK014(pha)002:254: 'phags mchog spyan sngar ji ltar dam bcas pa //
NK014(pha)002:255: sun par mi bgyi mgon khyod bslu ma lags //
NK014(pha)002:256: snying nas bdag ni khe dang grags la sogs //
NK014(pha)002:257: g.yo dang zang zing sems ni gtan spangs nas //
NK014(pha)002:258: gzhan don sgrub pa gcig pu'i sems bzhag ste //
NK014(pha)002:259: rnal 'byor spyod pa chen po bdag gis spyad //
NK014(pha)002:260: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yis //
NK014(pha)002:261: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK014(pha)002:262: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK014(pha)002:263: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK014(pha)002:264: srog chags thams cad gal te bdud gyur nas //
NK014(pha)002:265: dum bu stong du bdag gi lus gtub kyang //
NK014(pha)002:266: byang chub sems mchog shes rab snying rje dang //
NK014(pha)002:267: yi dam rgyal ba khyed ni yongs mi spong //
NK014(pha)002:268: rdo rje dam tshig chen po rnams dang ni //
NK014(pha)002:269: rdo rje slob dpon rdo rje mched lcam dang //
NK014(pha)002:270: gzhan yang theg pa mchog la zhugs pa rnams //
NK014(pha)002:271: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong ci nus bsrung //
NK014(pha)002:272: 'khor ba bdag med sgyu ma'i rang bzhin la //
NK014(pha)002:273: bdag ni 'jigs pa ci yang ma mchis te //
NK014(pha)002:274: ma rig skye bo rnams kyi don slad du //
NK014(pha)002:275: phyi mthar thug gi bar du gnas par spro //
NK014(pha)002:276: gzhan don 'khor ba rnams su spyod pa na //
NK014(pha)002:277: byang chub spyod pa rlabs chen bdag gis spyad //
NK014(pha)002:278: 'gro drug sems can rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK014(pha)002:279: rang dbang du ni skye ba blang bar bgyi //
NK014(pha)002:280: bdag ni yongs su bzung ba'i 'jig rten nam //
NK014(pha)002:281: mya ngan 'das la spro ba ma mchis te //
NK014(pha)002:282: gang dang gang du sdug bsngal gnas rnams su //
NK014(pha)002:283: bskal pa rgya mtshor gnas shing phan par bgyi //
NK014(pha)002:284: srid par yun ring dus su brtson pa ni //
NK014(pha)002:285: byang chub sems dpa'i yi dam lags pas na //
NK014(pha)002:286: ji srid ngan song stongs par ma gyur pa //
NK014(pha)002:287: de srid bdag gis skyo ba'i sems mi bskyed //
NK014(pha)002:288: shes rab thabs kyis 'gro ba'i don bgyid pa //
NK014(pha)002:289: snying rje'i longs spyod de las ma mchis pas //
NK014(pha)002:290: sems dmyal yi dwags gshin rje'i 'jig rten yang //
NK014(pha)002:291: lha yi dga' tshal lta bur blta bar bgyi //
NK014(pha)002:292: 'gro la thugs brtses dpal gyi mgur nas gsungs //
NK014(pha)002:293: rnal 'byor dam chos bdud rtsi mchog rnams ni //
NK014(pha)002:294: bdag gis 'jig rten thug pa ma mchis bar //
NK014(pha)002:295: ji ltar 'tshams pa bzhin du rgyas par bgyi //
NK014(pha)002:296: srid par las dang rkyen gyis dbang gyur te //
NK014(pha)002:297: gang dang gang du dam chos 'jig pa der //
NK014(pha)002:298: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NK014(pha)002:299: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bzung //
NK014(pha)002:300: bla med byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de //
NK014(pha)002:301: sgrub pa mchog la zhugs pa'i skye bo la //
NK014(pha)002:302: tshe rabs rnams su mthu rtsal ci mchis kyis //
NK014(pha)002:303: skyes chen rnams kyi dgongs pa rtag tu bskang //
NK014(pha)002:304: dam pa'i chos dang sgrub pa'i gegs gyur pa //
NK014(pha)002:305: mi dang mi min gdug pa gang yang rung //
NK014(pha)002:306: bdag gis zhi dang khro bo'i phrin las kyis //
NK014(pha)002:307: yongs su zhi zhing rnam par gzhom par bgyi //
NK014(pha)002:308: rnal 'byor mchog gi theg chen bla med dang //
NK014(pha)002:309: rdo rje rgyal po khyed la brten nas ni //
NK014(pha)002:310: sangs rgyas zhing sbyang 'gro la sman slad du //
NK014(pha)002:311: byang chub snying po bdag gis rtogs par bgyi //
NK014(pha)002:312: bdag ni 'phags mchog phyag rgya mngon sprul te //
NK014(pha)002:313: gal te skabs med 'chi ba'i dus byung tshe //
NK014(pha)002:314: gsang sngags mgon po ye shes dkyil 'khor can //
NK014(pha)002:315: khyed kyi zhabs kyi drung du mchi bar bgyi //
NK014(pha)002:316: srid gsum sdug bsngal ci 'dra khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK014(pha)002:317: dmyal sogs me dpung zhi bar bgyid la sogs //
NK014(pha)002:318: sems can don la myur du bdag mchi na //
NK014(pha)002:319: dam pa rnams kyis nus mthu stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)002:320: drug pa byin dbab pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:321: ye shes kyi 'khor lo thams cad mkha' khyab tu sad par byas la /
NK014(pha)002:322: h+aum a la la hoh b+ha ga w+aan sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)002:323: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK014(pha)002:324: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab /
NK014(pha)002:325: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i byin gyis rlob pa'i dbang mchog
NK014(pha)002:326: bskur ba'i dngos grub stsol ba'i mthu chen bdud 'dul
NK014(pha)002:327: bcom ldan 'das // byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK014(pha)002:328: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom dngos grub mchog stsol bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:329: rol mo sna tshogs kyi sgra sbyar zhing /
NK014(pha)002:330: h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum gis bsdus pas /
NK014(pha)002:331: nam mkha' gang ba'i lha tshogs thams cad bdag gnas yo byad rnams la thim ste /
NK014(pha)002:332: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor los byin gyis brlabs par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)002:333: bdun pa mchod rdzas byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:335: ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai sarba dra byam bi shwa d+ha ne h+aum phata kyis bsang /
NK014(pha)002:336: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham gis sbyang /
NK014(pha)002:337: stong pa'i ngang las rang nyid rdor sems su gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h+aum las /
NK014(pha)002:344: nam mkha'i khams thams cad khyab /
NK014(pha)002:346: 'khor 'das kyi rtsi bcud thams cad bsdus nas mchod rdzas rnams la thim par gyur /
NK014(pha)002:347: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ga ga na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK014(pha)002:348: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK014(pha)002:351: bde mchog sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba chen po'i rol pa las /
NK014(pha)002:352: rdo rje zhabs bsil ma la sogs pa mchod pa'i
NK014(pha)002:353: lha mo khrus gzhong dang spos khang man+d+ha ra'i me
NK014(pha)002:354: tog la sogs pa thogs pas nam mkha' gang ba
NK014(pha)002:355: rnams su gyur par bsam pas byin gyis brlabs /
NK014(pha)002:358: stong pa'i ngang las rang gi thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum chad /
NK014(pha)002:359: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK014(pha)002:360: bdud rtsi'i snod gzhal yas khang du gsal ba'i dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i lte bar /
NK014(pha)002:361: mi sha dang byang sems dkar po /
NK014(pha)002:362: shar du ba lang gi sha dang dri chen /
NK014(pha)002:363: lhor khyi sha dang sha chen /
NK014(pha)002:364: nub tu rta sha dang rak+ta /
NK014(pha)002:365: byang du glang po che'i sha dang dri chu rnams kyi steng du /
NK014(pha)002:371: h+aa t+aam rnams kyis mtshan par gyur /
NK014(pha)002:374: 'od zer 'phros 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK014(pha)002:379: ral gri so so'i rigs kyi dril bu rnams su gyur /
NK014(pha)002:382: dbus su mi bskyod pa yab yum mthing ga /
NK014(pha)002:385: shar du rnam snang yab yum dkar po /
NK014(pha)002:388: lhor rin 'byung yab yum ser po /
NK014(pha)002:391: nub tu snang mtha' yab yum dmar po /
NK014(pha)002:394: byang du don grub yab yum ljang gu rnams su gyur /
NK014(pha)002:396: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa go ham /
NK014(pha)002:397: a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK014(pha)002:398: dzahh+aum bam hoh bo d+hi tsit+ta /
NK014(pha)002:401: rigs lnga yab yum rjes chags kyi sbyor bas zhu
NK014(pha)002:402: ba las byung ba'i ye shes kyi bdud rtsi gyis
NK014(pha)002:403: mtshan pa'i kha gcod rdo rje rgya gram gyi lte
NK014(pha)002:404: bar / pad+m+aan+ta krita badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:405: rta mgrin dmar po pad+ma dang rdo rje rgya gram 'dzin pa lte ba yan chad thon pa /
NK014(pha)002:407: shar du mi pham ma dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)002:408: lhor khro gnyer ma ser mo zhags pa nub tu
NK014(pha)002:409: ro langs ma dmar mo lcags sgrog byang du ral
NK014(pha)002:410: gcig ma ljang gu dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)002:411: gyi 'od zer gyis 'khor 'das kyi bdud rtsi thams cad bkug /
NK014(pha)002:412: dam tshig gi bdud rtsi dang gnyis su med par gyur pa las /
NK014(pha)002:413: ye shes kyi bdud rtsi rgya mtsho chen por gyur par bsam la /
NK014(pha)002:414: g.yon pa'i mtheb srin gyi rdo rjes bdud rtsi la reg ste /
NK014(pha)002:415: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK014(pha)002:417: mthar g.yon bskor du dkrugs te /
NK014(pha)002:418: h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes brjod pas /
NK014(pha)002:419: yum bzhi bdud rtsi la thim par bsam mo /
NK014(pha)002:422: stong pa nyid kyi ngang las /
NK014(pha)002:423: b+h+r+aum pad+ma ba lim ta bi shwa tsakra b+h+r+aum /
NK014(pha)002:424: gtor gzhong pad+ma'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du /
NK014(pha)002:425: gtor rdzas 'dod yon gyi rnam pa ma tshang ba med pa la gyis mtshan par gyur /
NK014(pha)002:428: ba lim ta te dz+wa ba lim ta ba la b+aa d+ya gu h+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK014(pha)002:430: gzugs rdo rje ma sogs lha mo nam mkha' gang
NK014(pha)002:431: bas 'dod yon dpag tu med par spro ba'i bdag
NK014(pha)002:434: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum b+hany+dza ka p+aa la b+h+r+aum /
NK014(pha)002:435: dmar gyi dung chen yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang
NK014(pha)002:436: du rak+ta la ra yig dmar pos mtshan par gyur
NK014(pha)002:439: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK014(pha)002:440: chags med rak+ta'i rgya mtsho rba rlabs 'khrug pas nam mkha' gang bar bsam mo //
NK014(pha)002:442: khyad par gyi sbyor ba dgos ched kyi sgo nas sems bskyed pa dang /
NK014(pha)002:443: ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos gnyis /
NK014(pha)002:445: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad gdugs pa can gyi
NK014(pha)002:446: yul la thugs rje chen pos cher khros nas 'dul
NK014(pha)002:448: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa'i 'gro ba rnams la
NK014(pha)002:449: rjes su chags pa'i snying rje chen po rdo rje
NK014(pha)002:450: khro bo'i sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi
NK014(pha)002:451: 'khor lo'i dkyil 'khor du ldang bar bagyi'o snyam pas
NK014(pha)002:452: / 'dzin pa'i dbang gis sdug bsngal zhing //
NK014(pha)002:453: gdug pa srid gsum 'dul ba dang //
NK014(pha)002:454: nga rgyal chen po brtan pa'i phyir //
NK014(pha)002:456: zhes pas dam 'cha' zhing sems bskyed do //
NK014(pha)002:457: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos la /
NK014(pha)002:458: ting 'dzin gsum gyis khog dbub pa /
NK014(pha)002:459: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK014(pha)002:460: las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang gsum /
NK014(pha)002:463: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK014(pha)002:464: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK014(pha)002:465: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK014(pha)002:466: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK014(pha)002:467: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad dmigs med spros
NK014(pha)002:468: pa dang bral ba'i stong pa nyid du bsgom pa'o
NK014(pha)002:470: e ma'o kun tu bzang po ni //
NK014(pha)002:471: bde chen spros bral thig le las //
NK014(pha)002:472: stong pa nyid du rab gsal ba'i //
NK014(pha)002:473: snying rje'i yul ni bsgom par bya //
NK014(pha)002:474: de bzhin nyid ma rtogs pa'i sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK014(pha)002:475: sems can rnams la 'dzin med sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK014(pha)002:476: snying rje mkha' khyab kun tu snang bar bsgom pa'o
NK014(pha)002:478: nges pa las ni rdo rje che //
NK014(pha)002:479: de las dpal chen he ru ka /
NK014(pha)002:480: 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgu yis //
NK014(pha)002:481: 'jigs pa yi ni dus ltar drag /
NK014(pha)002:483: rang rig snang stong gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin h+aum yig mthing ga gsal zhing 'bar bar gyur /
NK014(pha)002:485: de las 'od zer h+aum gi rnam pa nam mkha' gang bar 'phros /
NK014(pha)002:488: mkha' khyab kyi h+aum rnams gzhi'i h+aum la thim /
NK014(pha)002:492: rdo rje sngon po rtse dgu par gyur /
NK014(pha)002:498: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:500: rgyu'i he ru ka sku mdog smug nag cir yang 'gyur ba /
NK014(pha)002:501: rdo rje dang dung khrag 'dzin pa 'bar ba'i gar dgu dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)002:503: rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa dang /
NK014(pha)002:504: brten pa lha bsgom pa gnyis kyi /
NK014(pha)002:506: dang po bzhi dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:507: rgyu'i he ru ka'i thugs ka'i h+aum las /
NK014(pha)002:508: e yam ra sum kem ram rnams chad /
NK014(pha)002:511: 'phros 'dus 'od du zhu ba las rim pa bzhin /
NK014(pha)002:513: e las nam mkha' chos kyi 'byung gnas gru gsum 'byams klas pa'i dbyings su /
NK014(pha)002:515: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor ljang gu rgya gram g.yo ba'i ba dan gyis mtshan pa /
NK014(pha)002:516: ra rak+ta sa mu dra man+da la /
NK014(pha)002:517: ra las rak+ta'i rgya mtsho dmar po zlum po rba rlabs 'khrug pa /
NK014(pha)002:519: sum las zhing chen gyi sa gzhi gru bzhi pa /
NK014(pha)002:520: kem ni ri ti man+da la /
NK014(pha)002:521: kem las keng rus kyi ri rab sngo skya gru bzhi bang rim bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK014(pha)002:523: ram las me'i dkyil 'khor dmar nag nam mkha'i mtha' klas par 'bar bar bsam la /
NK014(pha)002:524: dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa //
NK014(pha)002:525: khrag gi rgya mtsho 'khrug pa'i dkyil //
NK014(pha)002:526: keng rus chen po'i ri rab kyi //
NK014(pha)002:527: steng gi 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK014(pha)002:529: de dag kyang phyi ltar na 'byung ba lnga /
NK014(pha)002:530: nang ltar na ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin /
NK014(pha)002:531: gsang ba ltar na yum lnga'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa'o //
NK014(pha)002:532: gnyis pa rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa dngos ni /
NK014(pha)002:533: ri rab kyi steng du rgyu'i h+aum las b+h+r+aum smug nag chad /
NK014(pha)002:536: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la /
NK014(pha)002:537: ye shes rin po che'i rang bzhin b+hany+dza 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa /
NK014(pha)002:538: phyi nang nyis rim 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis dang
NK014(pha)002:539: ldan pa'i phyi ma'i rtsig pa rim pa lnga dang
NK014(pha)002:540: / nang rtsig rim pa gsum pa ste /
NK014(pha)002:541: gnyis ka'ang thod pa skam rnying rlon gsum khrag zhag
NK014(pha)002:542: gi 'dam gyis brtsigs shing gnam lcags u rmo'i gzer
NK014(pha)002:544: thod pa sna tshogs pas bkra ba'i pha gu 'phyar
NK014(pha)002:545: thabs su bkod pa las rgyu ma dang don snying
NK014(pha)002:547: de'i steng du bre phul gyi snam bu la ma
NK014(pha)002:548: ka ra'i kha nas sbrul sbram dang thod skam gyi
NK014(pha)002:549: d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa /
NK014(pha)002:550: don snying dang yan lag gi 'phyang phrul /
NK014(pha)002:552: lcang lo'i rnga yab dang dril g.yer rlung gis bskyod pas mdzes shing /
NK014(pha)002:553: phyi ngos su bya 'dab las 'phyang ba'i rkang lag gi shar bu /
NK014(pha)002:554: steng ngos su sgal tshigs kyi mda' yab tshar du dngar ba /
NK014(pha)002:555: de dag gi bar bar du zhing chen gyi gdugs /
NK014(pha)002:558: zhing lpags kyi lhab lhub sogs 'jigs pa'i rgyan sna tshogs pas bkra ba /
NK014(pha)002:559: rim pa gnyis ka'i rtsig pa'i phyi 'gram nas 'dod
NK014(pha)002:560: yon gyi snam bu dmar pos bskor ba la gzugs
NK014(pha)002:561: rdo rje ma sogs lha mo rnams kyis dur khrod
NK014(pha)002:562: rol pa'i mchod sprin rab 'byams spro ba /
NK014(pha)002:563: sgo dang sgo 'khyud kyi mtshams dang zur bzhir zla phyed rdo rjes mtshan pa /
NK014(pha)002:564: phyi ma'i sgo logs kyi phyi zur bzhi nas zhing
NK014(pha)002:565: gi ka ba bzhi bzhis btegs pa'i rta babs snam
NK014(pha)002:566: bu brgyad pa so dang thod pa dang dbang po
NK014(pha)002:567: dang nyi zla'i phreng ba rnams kyis spras shing bsil
NK014(pha)002:568: khang dang ldan pa'i rtser pad+ma la gnas pa'i chos
NK014(pha)002:569: kyi 'khor lo'i steng nas zhing gi gdugs phub cing
NK014(pha)002:570: / chu srin phru gu zung gis brten pa /
NK014(pha)002:571: phyi nang gi sgo thams cad la rus sbal gyi ma them /
NK014(pha)002:574: zhing gi sgo glegs rnams kyis spras pa /
NK014(pha)002:575: sgo phyi ma'i g.yas g.yon gyi gzhi la skyes bu gsal shing gis phug pa dang /
NK014(pha)002:576: t+aa la'i ljon pa rnams thod tshal rgyu ma la brgyus pa'i phreng bas bres shing /
NK014(pha)002:577: rak+ta'i rdzing bu rlabs phreng 'khrug pa brgyad kyis bskor ba /
NK014(pha)002:578: dkyil 'khor de'i nang gi khyams phyi ma khrag mtsho dang /
NK014(pha)002:579: nang ma gser khyams su gnas pa /
NK014(pha)002:580: thod skam gyis brtsigs pa'i gru chad bzhi glo 'bur
NK014(pha)002:581: gyis mdzes pa'i steng du 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte
NK014(pha)002:582: ba dang bcas pa rnams rim pa bzhin khyad par
NK014(pha)002:584: nang lha chen po brgyad kyi ka ba rus sbal
NK014(pha)002:585: gyi ka gdan dang ldan pas btegs pa'i steng na
NK014(pha)002:586: tshangs pa'i gdung bzhi gdung zlum dang bcas pa /
NK014(pha)002:588: rgyu skar gyi dral grab zhing lpags kyi thog phub
NK014(pha)002:589: nyi zla'i mthongs skar dang bcas pa'i dbus phyur bu
NK014(pha)002:590: lha chen po'i thod pas zlum por phub pa'i rtse
NK014(pha)002:591: mor tsit+ta'i tog gis brgyan pa /
NK014(pha)002:592: nang gi steng 'og rnams shar dkar /
NK014(pha)002:597: 'bar ba'i phreng ba 'khrug cing 'bar ba la sogs
NK014(pha)002:598: te dur khrod rol pa'i gzhal yas khang gi mtshan
NK014(pha)002:600: dwangs shing sgrib pa med par kun tu gsal ba /
NK014(pha)002:601: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo'i lte
NK014(pha)002:602: ba la rdzogs pa'i phyi rol srung ba'i khor yug
NK014(pha)002:603: gi nang du ru dra longs spyod dang bcas pa
NK014(pha)002:604: dbyings su bsgral ba'i dur khrod chen po brgyad /
NK014(pha)002:606: de'i rtsa ba la gnas pa'i phyogs skyong brgyad /
NK014(pha)002:607: yal ga la brten pa'i zhing skyong brgyad /
NK014(pha)002:609: de la rol pa'i klu brgyad /
NK014(pha)002:615: mchod rten rnams kyang brgyad brgyad /
NK014(pha)002:616: thams cad du grub pa dang rig 'dzin /
NK014(pha)002:617: dpa' bo dang rnal 'byor ma'i tshogs dang /
NK014(pha)002:618: ro langs dang sha za 'byung po'i tshogs rnams ha har rgod cing gar rtse ba /
NK014(pha)002:619: bya dang gcan gzan gtum po mang po lang long du rgyu zhing /
NK014(pha)002:625: 'thor ba la sogs pa'i sha rus gsar rnying sna
NK014(pha)002:626: tshogs pa gcal du bkram zhing phung por spungs pas
NK014(pha)002:627: yongs su gang bar bsam zhing /
NK014(pha)002:628: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK014(pha)002:629: phyogs bcur rgya yongs ma chad pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:630: phyi dang nang med kun tu nang //
NK014(pha)002:632: gru chad bzhis ni rnam par brgyan //
NK014(pha)002:633: gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan //
NK014(pha)002:634: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis kyis mdzes //
NK014(pha)002:635: thod sbrul sna tshogs nyi zlas brjid //
NK014(pha)002:638: gsum pa gdan bskyed pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:639: gzhal yas khang gi dbus kyi lte ba dang /
NK014(pha)002:644: sna tshogs pad+ma'i lte bar zla ba dang nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor brtsegs pa re re /
NK014(pha)002:652: dbus su lha chen po dbang phyug dang drag po /
NK014(pha)002:656: byang du gnod sbyin rnams rang rang gi chung ma dang bcas pa'i pho rnams kha sbub dang /
NK014(pha)002:657: mo rnams gan rkyal byi chings su bsnol ba /
NK014(pha)002:663: byang du stag rnams zung re res pho rnams kyi sog phrag dang /
NK014(pha)002:664: mo rnams kyi nu phrag nas nan tur du bardzisa pa /
NK014(pha)002:667: khyams nang ma'i phyogs mtshams brgyad /
NK014(pha)002:671: nyi ma la gnas pa'i zhing gi gdan re re /
NK014(pha)002:672: khyams phyi ma'i phyogs rer drug drug dang /
NK014(pha)002:675: zhing skam po'i gdan rkyang pa re re /
NK014(pha)002:676: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK014(pha)002:677: gtum pa dom gyi spar bas ni //
NK014(pha)002:678: dbang phyug lha chen la sogs bzung //
NK014(pha)002:680: gnyis pa brten pa lha bskyed pa la gnyis te /
NK014(pha)002:684: he ru kar bskyed nas snyoms 'jug bya ba dang /
NK014(pha)002:685: ngo mtshar sras kyi dkyil 'khor spro ba'o //
NK014(pha)002:687: nam mkhar gnas pa'i rgyu'i he ru ka dbus kyi gdan la bzhugs pa las /
NK014(pha)002:688: de nyid dpal chen po sku mdog smug nag cir yang 'gyur ba /
NK014(pha)002:689: dbu dang phyag zhabs stong khams kyi rdul snyed mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin par gyur te /
NK014(pha)002:690: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid nas khro mo dbang phyug chen mo mngon du phyungs te /
NK014(pha)002:691: hi hi zhes dgyes pa'i mdangs kyis yab la btud cing /
NK014(pha)002:693: gnyis su med par 'khril ba'i dgyes pas rol par bsam la /
NK014(pha)002:694: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK014(pha)002:695: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK014(pha)002:696: khro rgyal ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK014(pha)002:697: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas ni //
NK014(pha)002:698: khro mo dbang phyug mngon phyungs te //
NK014(pha)002:699: hi hi dgyes pa'i gzi mdangs kyis //
NK014(pha)002:700: rin chen pad+ma rgyas mdzad de //
NK014(pha)002:701: gnyis med 'khril bas dgyes par thim //
NK014(pha)002:704: sngags kyi sprul pa spro ba /
NK014(pha)002:706: sras mo nyi shu bskyed pa'o //
NK014(pha)002:708: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata phata /
NK014(pha)002:709: ha la ha la ha la h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:711: yab yum gnyis kyi sbyor mtshams nas byang chub sems kyi sprin las /
NK014(pha)002:712: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas khyab pa /
NK014(pha)002:713: khro bo 'chol ba mtshon cha sna tshogs kyi char 'bebs pa dpag tu med pa spros /
NK014(pha)002:714: ltas chen po bco lngas gdug pa can gyi tshogs thams cad tshar bcad par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)002:716: mkha' khyab kyi khro bo'i sprin rnams slar 'dus pa las /
NK014(pha)002:717: rdo rje rigs kyi khro bo rnams rang la thim pas 'bras bu'i he ru kar gyur pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:718: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:719: badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)002:720: bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po badz+ra
NK014(pha)002:721: he ru ka sku mdog mthing nag char sprin ltar
NK014(pha)002:722: gnag cing / nyi ma bye ba'i gzi byin 'bar ba /
NK014(pha)002:723: dbu gsum gyi g.yas zhal dkar la bzhad pa /
NK014(pha)002:724: g.yon zhal dmar la gshe ba /
NK014(pha)002:725: dbus zhal mthing nag drag por khros pa'i nyams can /
NK014(pha)002:726: zhal re re la dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum gsum dang ldan pa /
NK014(pha)002:727: rnam par 'gyur ba'i zhal gdangs shing /
NK014(pha)002:730: rdo rje'i gad mos sa gsum g.yo ba /
NK014(pha)002:731: khro gnyer bsdus pa'i shangs nas mi bzad pa'i h+aum sgra 'byin pa /
NK014(pha)002:732: rdzi smin sma ra las 'bar ba'i me 'khyog por spro ba /
NK014(pha)002:733: sku che zhing yan lag rags pa /
NK014(pha)002:734: lang tsho rgyas pa'i 'gyur bag can /
NK014(pha)002:735: rdo rje'i ba spus gtams pa /
NK014(pha)002:736: sgeg pa dpa' ba mi sdug pa /
NK014(pha)002:737: rgod dang gshe dang 'jigs su rung /
NK014(pha)002:738: snying rje rngams dang zhi ba ste /
NK014(pha)002:739: gar gyi nyams dgus rab tu rgyas pa /
NK014(pha)002:740: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis /
NK014(pha)002:741: rdo rje rtse dgu dang dril bu 'dzin pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK014(pha)002:742: gnyis pas rdo rje rtse lnga dang /
NK014(pha)002:743: b+hany+dza dmar gyis gang ba thogs pa /
NK014(pha)002:744: gsum pas zhing gi dbyug pa dang stong gi 'jig rten 'degs pa /
NK014(pha)002:746: g.yon bskum pa'i gyad chen po'i stabs kyis rang gi stan la rol ba /
NK014(pha)002:747: dbu re re la thod pa skam po lnga lnga rigs lnga'i cod pan can gyis dbu brgyan pa /
NK014(pha)002:748: 'dzag pa'i mgo bo lnga bcu'i do shal dang /
NK014(pha)002:749: thod pa tshal bu'i dpung rgyan can /
NK014(pha)002:750: zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang /
NK014(pha)002:751: glang po che'i ko ba rlon pas stod g.yogs shing /
NK014(pha)002:752: stag gi lpags pa'i sham thabs grol ba /
NK014(pha)002:753: klu rgyal rigs dkar pos skra chings /
NK014(pha)002:754: rje rigs ser pos snyan cha /
NK014(pha)002:755: bram ze'i rigs dmar pos se mo do dang mgur chu /
NK014(pha)002:756: dmangs rigs ljang khus ska rags dang do shal /
NK014(pha)002:757: gdol pa nag pos phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu ste /
NK014(pha)002:758: thams cad kyang gdug pa sbrul gyi rnam pa can /
NK014(pha)002:759: dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu /
NK014(pha)002:760: smin mtshams su rak+ta'i thig le /
NK014(pha)002:761: mgrin par zhag gi zo ris kyis mtshan pa ste dur khrod rol pa'i chas brgyad dang /
NK014(pha)002:762: dpal gyi chas bcu sku la rdzogs shing /
NK014(pha)002:763: snyan gong nas nyi zla'i 'od zer spro ba /
NK014(pha)002:764: yum kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma sngo skya zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum /
NK014(pha)002:765: gcer bu skra grol zhing lang tshos sgeg pa'i nyams gyur can /
NK014(pha)002:766: g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK014(pha)002:767: g.yon thod pa khrag gis gang ba gtso bo'i zhal du stob pa /
NK014(pha)002:768: gzig gi lpags pa'i sham thabs sogs dur khrod rol pa'i chas can /
NK014(pha)002:770: g.yas bskum pas gtso bo dang dgyes par 'khril ba /
NK014(pha)002:771: stong pa nyid dang snying rje chen po zung du 'jug pa'i bdag nyid can /
NK014(pha)002:772: bskal pa'i me'i phung po rab tu 'bar ba'i klong
NK014(pha)002:773: na khams gsum pa'i dbang phyug chen po'i ngo bor
NK014(pha)002:775: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK014(pha)002:778: las kyi rigs kyi khro bo'i tshogs rnams so sor
NK014(pha)002:779: 'dus pa las rigs bzhi'i he ru ka'i skur gyur
NK014(pha)002:780: nas 'khor lo'i rtsibs bzhir rang rang gi gdan la
NK014(pha)002:781: bzhugs pa ni / bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:782: bud+d+ha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)002:783: shar gyi rtsibs la bud+d+ha he ru ka sku dang rtsa zhal smug nag /
NK014(pha)002:784: g.yas dkar g.yon ser ba'i zhal gsum /
NK014(pha)002:785: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK014(pha)002:786: gnyis pas rdo rje dang dung khrag /
NK014(pha)002:787: tha mas zhing dbyug dang tri sh+au la 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)002:788: yum bud+d+ha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma smug nag dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK014(pha)002:789: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:790: rat+na kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)002:791: lho'i rtsibs la rat+na he ru ka sku dang rtsa zhal ser nag /
NK014(pha)002:792: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar ba'i zhal gsum /
NK014(pha)002:793: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis rin po che dang dril bu /
NK014(pha)002:794: gnyis pas rdo rje dang dung khrag /
NK014(pha)002:795: tha mas zhing dbyug dang dgra s+t+wa 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)002:796: yum rat+na kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma ser mo dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK014(pha)002:797: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:798: pad+ma kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)002:799: nub kyi rtsibs la pad+ma he ru ka sku dang rtsa zhal dmar nag /
NK014(pha)002:800: g.yas dkar g.yon ser ba'i zhal gsum /
NK014(pha)002:801: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK014(pha)002:802: gnyis pas rdo rje dang dung khrag /
NK014(pha)002:803: tha mas zhing dbyug dang rnge'u chung 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)002:804: yum pad+ma kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma dmar mo dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK014(pha)002:805: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK014(pha)002:806: karma kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)002:807: byang gi rtsibs la karma he ru ka sku dang rtsa zhal ljang nag /
NK014(pha)002:808: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar ba'i zhal gsum /
NK014(pha)002:809: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis rgya gram dang dril bu /
NK014(pha)002:810: gnyis pas rdo rje dang dung khrag /
NK014(pha)002:811: tha mas zhing dbyug dang thong gshol 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)002:812: yum karma kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma ljang mo dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK014(pha)002:813: khrag 'thung yab yum thams cad kyang gar dgu'i ros sgeg cing /
NK014(pha)002:814: rgyan dang cha lugs gtso bo dang mthun pa /
NK014(pha)002:815: rang rang gi gdan la g.yas brkyang pa'i stabs kyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK014(pha)002:817: de nas rigs lnga'i khrag 'thung yab yum rnams rjes su chags pa'i sbyor bas snyoms par zhugs te /
NK014(pha)002:818: dgyes pa'i bzhad sgra ha zhes brjod pas /
NK014(pha)002:819: sbyor mtshams nas byang chub kyi sems sprin khro mo brgyad kyi rnam par thon nas rigs bsdus te /
NK014(pha)002:820: 'khor lo'i grwa dang gru chad bzhir rang rang gi gdan la bzhugs pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:821: rtsibs mchan gyi shar lhor goo r+ai ma sngon mo g.yas zhing dbyug dang g.yon b+han dmar 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)002:822: lho nub tu tsoo r+ai ma ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa /
NK014(pha)002:823: nub byang du pra mo ha dmar mo chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan 'phyar ba /
NK014(pha)002:824: byang shar du be ta li nag mo g.yas rdo rje 'phyar zhing g.yon byis pa'i bam za ba /
NK014(pha)002:825: gru chad kyi shar lhor puk+ka s+ai dmar ser zhing chung gi rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK014(pha)002:826: lho nub tu g+hasma ljang gu g.yas pa'i rdo rjes g.yon gyi dung dmar dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK014(pha)002:827: nub byang du sma sha mthing nag byis pa'i ro bzung nas snying za ba /
NK014(pha)002:828: byang shar du tsan+da ser skya mchog lus 'dral ba /
NK014(pha)002:829: thams cad kyang zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa /
NK014(pha)002:831: skra ser po gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK014(pha)002:832: gcer bu dur khrod rol pa'i chas can /
NK014(pha)002:833: g.yon brkyang ba'i stabs kyis gnas pa'o //
NK014(pha)002:834: de nas sngar bzhin dgyes pa'i bzhad sgra he zhes brjod pas /
NK014(pha)002:835: byang chub kyi sems sprin phra men brgyad kyi rnam par thon nas rigs bsdus te /
NK014(pha)002:836: gser khyams kyi phyogs mtshams brgyad du rang rang gi gdan la bzhugs pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:837: shar du seng gdong ma ser mo phyag gnyis thugs
NK014(pha)002:838: kar gyen du bsnol bas ti ra bzung nas za
NK014(pha)002:839: ba / lhor stag gdong ma dmar mo phyag gnyis mthur du bsnol nas ro bzung ba /
NK014(pha)002:840: nub tu wa gdong ma nag mo zhing chung bzung nas lces ldag pa /
NK014(pha)002:841: byang du spyang gdong ma mthing ga zhing chung gi
NK014(pha)002:842: khog pa 'dral ba ste mche ba can bzhi dang
NK014(pha)002:843: / shar lhor bzhad gdong ma dmar ser g.yon zhing
NK014(pha)002:844: chung bzung ba'i rgyu ma g.yas pas drangs nas gsol
NK014(pha)002:845: / ba / lho nub tu kang+ka'i mgo can dmar
NK014(pha)002:846: skya bam ro'i rkang lag bzung nas phrag par 'gel
NK014(pha)002:847: / ba / ba / nub byang du bya rog
NK014(pha)002:848: gdong can nag mo g.yas ral gri g.yon b+han dmar
NK014(pha)002:850: du 'ug gdong ma mthing ga g.yas lcags kyu dang
NK014(pha)002:851: g.yon b+han dmar 'dzin pa ste gshog pa can bzhi
NK014(pha)002:853: cad kyang gcer bu rang rang khros pa'i zhal can
NK014(pha)002:854: drag mo'i rnam 'gyur dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas dang
NK014(pha)002:856: pa'o // slar yang dgyes pa'i bzhad sgra phata ces
NK014(pha)002:858: pa'o // brjod pas / byang chub kyi sems sprin
NK014(pha)002:859: sgo skyong bzhi'i rnam par thon nas rigs bsdus te
NK014(pha)002:860: sgo bzhir rang rang gi gdan la bzhugs pa ni
NK014(pha)002:862: pa'o // brjod pas / / shar sgor rta gdong
NK014(pha)002:863: ma sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)002:864: lho sgor phag gdong ma nag mo mche zhags 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)002:865: nub sgor seng gdong ma dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)002:866: byang sgor spyang gdong ma ljang gu'i dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)002:867: bzhi ka'ang gcer bu gtum zhing khros pa'i nyams can dur khrod kyi chas kyis brgyan te /
NK014(pha)002:869: de ltar gtso 'khor thams cad sku mdog phyag mtshan /
NK014(pha)002:870: rgyan dang cha lugs rnams gsal zhing gzi brjid dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)002:871: gnyis pa gzhan sras kyi cho ga la /
NK014(pha)002:872: snang ba'i zhen pa sbyong ba dang /
NK014(pha)002:873: stong pa'i 'dzin pa sbyong ba gnyis /
NK014(pha)002:874: dang po snang zhen sbyong ba la'ang /
NK014(pha)002:877: gsal gdab pa dang gsum gyi /
NK014(pha)002:879: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas kun tu bzang po byang
NK014(pha)002:880: chub kyi sems kyi bdag nyid rnam smin gyi lus
NK014(pha)002:882: dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgor 'dud pa'i rnam pas 'khod par bsam zhing //
NK014(pha)002:883: sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni //
NK014(pha)002:884: 'jig rten ma lus thams cad kun //
NK014(pha)002:885: rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyor bas na //
NK014(pha)002:886: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK014(pha)002:889: lha rnams kyiis rjes su gnang ste /
NK014(pha)002:890: thabs dang shes rab kyi 'od zer bdag la 'phros
NK014(pha)002:891: pas sems kyi rtog pa dang de las gyur pa'i
NK014(pha)002:893: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes gzung 'dzin dang bral
NK014(pha)002:894: ba'i rang bzhin gser zhun lta bu'i 'od kyi gong
NK014(pha)002:896: lha rnams kyi sku gsung thugs kyi 'od zer 'bru gsum gyi rnam par 'phros te thim pas /
NK014(pha)002:897: de nyid +aahh+aum gsum du gyur nas rim bzhin h+aum
NK014(pha)002:898: la zhugs pa zla ba dang rlung dkyil la gnas
NK014(pha)002:899: par gyur / de rlung gi btegs pas bung ba
NK014(pha)002:900: me tog la lding ba ltar lha tshogs thams cad
NK014(pha)002:901: la g.yas su lan gsum bskor nas gtso bo'i thugs
NK014(pha)002:902: par gyur / kar thim / yab yum snyoms par
NK014(pha)002:903: zhugs pa'i dga' ba'i rol mos byang chub kyi sems
NK014(pha)002:904: par gyur / kar thim / su zhu ba / sku'i dbyibs brgyud /
NK014(pha)002:905: rdo rje'i lam nas yum gyi pad+mara son pa 'od kyi gong bur gnas pa las /
NK014(pha)002:906: gtso bo yab yum kyang rjes su chags pa'i sbyor bas bde ba'i ngo bor zhu bar bsam mo /
NK014(pha)002:908: h+aum ha he phata ces brjod pas /
NK014(pha)002:912: sgo ma bzhi rnams rim bzhin dbus kyi thig le
NK014(pha)002:913: la ro gcig tu gyur pa las gser zhun lta
NK014(pha)002:914: bu'i 'od kyi gong bu 'bar bar bsam mo //
NK014(pha)002:916: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pas //
NK014(pha)002:917: ye shes zer gyis lus rtog sbyangs //
NK014(pha)002:918: gser zhun lta bu'i sems dag las //
NK014(pha)002:920: thugs kar thim nas sku yi dbyibs //
NK014(pha)002:921: rdo rje'i lam nas yum gyi mkhar //
NK014(pha)002:922: chos sku byang chub sems su gnas //
NK014(pha)002:923: lha rnams so so'i snying po'i sgra //
NK014(pha)002:924: h+aum ha he phata ces byung nas //
NK014(pha)002:925: byang chub sems su gcig par thim //
NK014(pha)002:927: gnyis pa stong pa'i 'dzin zhen sbyong ba la /
NK014(pha)002:931: gtso bo yab yum bskyed pa /
NK014(pha)002:932: yan lag gi lha bsgom pa /
NK014(pha)002:936: gdan steng gi 'od phung de nyid h+aum zung gcig tu gyur /
NK014(pha)002:938: de las 'od zer mkha' khyab tu 'phros /
NK014(pha)002:944: rdo rje rtse dgu dang dril bu h+aum yig gis mtshan par gyur /
NK014(pha)002:947: sngar bzhin 'phros 'dus 'od du zhu ba las /
NK014(pha)002:948: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:949: badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+aam /
NK014(pha)002:950: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po badz+ra he ru
NK014(pha)002:951: ka sku mdog mthing nag char sprin ltar gnag cing
NK014(pha)002:952: nyi ma bye ba'i gzi byin 'bar ba /
NK014(pha)002:954: khams gsum pa'i dbang phyug chen po'i ngo bor bzhugs pa'o //
NK014(pha)002:955: zhes pa'i bar sngar ltar brjod cing bsgom mo //
NK014(pha)002:957: rang gi thugs rin po che'i gur khyim lta bu'i
NK014(pha)002:958: nang du nyi ma la gnas pa'i rang 'dra ba'i
NK014(pha)002:960: de'i thugs kar ting 'dzin sems dpa' rdo rje rtse
NK014(pha)002:961: dgu pa'i lte bar h+aum yig phra mo 'bar bas
NK014(pha)002:963: de las 'od zer 'phros pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i
NK014(pha)002:964: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad dbang gi lha rigs
NK014(pha)002:965: lnga yab yum gyi rnam par badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs
NK014(pha)002:967: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)002:969: de rnams gnyis su med par sbyor ba mdzad /
NK014(pha)002:970: rjes chags kyi mes zhu ba'i ye shes lnga'i chu
NK014(pha)002:971: rgyun mgo bo'i gnas lngar babs te dbang bskur bar
NK014(pha)002:972: bsam zhing / rigs lnga'i dbang rgya spyi bo'i gnas lngar 'jog cing dbang sngags rnams brjod pa ste /
NK014(pha)002:973: rdo rje phyir bsdams las gung mo gnyis brkyang ba spyi bor bzhag la /
NK014(pha)002:974: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)002:975: phyag rgya de las mdzub mo gnyis brkyang ba dpral bar bzhag la /
NK014(pha)002:976: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)002:977: srin lag brkyang ba rna ltag g.yas par /
NK014(pha)002:978: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)002:979: mthe bong brkyang ba ltag par /
NK014(pha)002:980: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)002:981: mathe'u chung brkyang ba rna ltag g.yon par /
NK014(pha)002:982: ma h+aa kri t+y+aa nush+th+aa na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)002:983: zhes rim par dbang bskur bas /
NK014(pha)002:984: nyon mongs pa lnga'i dri ma sbyangs /
NK014(pha)002:985: phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su gnas bsgyur /
NK014(pha)002:986: chu'i lhag ma spyi bor brtan pa yongs su gyur
NK014(pha)002:987: pa las de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lngas dbu brgyan
NK014(pha)002:988: par bsam mo // spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i dkar po /
NK014(pha)002:989: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK014(pha)002:990: sku rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar bya'o //
NK014(pha)002:992: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK014(pha)002:993: yongs su gyur pa las rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo 'dzin pas rgyas btab par bsam zhing /
NK014(pha)002:994: rdo rje'i phyag rgya spyi bor gtugs la /
NK014(pha)002:995: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)002:996: mgrin par pad+ma la gnas pa'i +aam dmar po /
NK014(pha)002:997: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK014(pha)002:998: gsung rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK014(pha)002:1000: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung dang gnyis su med par gyur /
