NK014(pha)002:1677: brgyad pa rak+ta'i mchod pa la gsum las /
NK014(pha)002:1680: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK014(pha)002:1681: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK014(pha)002:1682: dpal chen 'khor bcas spyan drangs te //
NK014(pha)002:1683: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK014(pha)002:1684: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK014(pha)002:1687: ma lus bzhes nas bsnams su gsol //
NK014(pha)002:1688: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK014(pha)002:1693: sh+r+ai m+aan kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)002:1694: zhes dang po sbrengs pas rak+ta'i dwangs ma ye shes
NK014(pha)002:1695: kyi bdud rtsi'i ngo bor sum gcig rol bar bsam
NK014(pha)002:1698: nga ni khrag 'thung chen po ste //
NK014(pha)002:1699: 'khor ba'i d+r+wa bar chags pa yis //
NK014(pha)002:1700: dmar chen bskyil ba'i rgya mtsho la //
NK014(pha)002:1702: ma rungs 'dod la ma chags shing //
NK014(pha)002:1703: dam tshig la sdang dgra chen rnams //
NK014(pha)002:1704: thugs rje byang sems ldan pa yis //
NK014(pha)002:1705: ngo 'thon stobs kyis bsgral bar bya //
NK014(pha)002:1706: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK014(pha)002:1707: sarba dush+tana sa ma ya r+au dra m+aa ra ya /
NK014(pha)002:1708: kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)002:1709: hri da ya pi pa h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:1710: ces gnyis pa sbrengs pas rak+ta'i khu ba zhing bcu'i
NK014(pha)002:1711: dgra bgegs kyi ngo bor gnyis sum rol par bsam
NK014(pha)002:1714: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK014(pha)002:1715: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang //
NK014(pha)002:1716: gdul dka' ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)002:1717: sha rus la sogs za bar bya'o //
NK014(pha)002:1718: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya ma h+aa m+aam sa /
NK014(pha)002:1722: ma h+aa go ro tsa na /
NK014(pha)002:1723: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti /
NK014(pha)002:1724: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK014(pha)002:1725: ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hoh kha kha kha /
NK014(pha)002:1730: zhes gsum pa sbrengs pas rak+ta'i snyigs ma zhing bcu'i
NK014(pha)002:1731: dug gsum sha khrag rus pa'i dngos por lhag med
NK014(pha)002:1734: rang gi thugs ka nas ram dpag tu med pa chad /
NK014(pha)002:1736: ram las ye shes kyi me 'bar bas sems can
NK014(pha)002:1737: thams cad kyi snying nang na gnas pa'i rigs drug
NK014(pha)002:1738: gi sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa bsregs /
NK014(pha)002:1739: rnam shes chos kyi dbyings su bsgral bar bsam zhing /
NK014(pha)002:1741: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK014(pha)002:1742: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK014(pha)002:1743: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK014(pha)002:1744: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK014(pha)002:1746: rang gi gsang gnas h+aum las ye shes kyi rdo
NK014(pha)002:1747: rje rtse mo lnga pa'i lte bar byang chub kyi
NK014(pha)002:1748: sems dkar por gnas pa'i bu gar phata kyis bkag
NK014(pha)002:1749: pa / yum gyi mkha' pam las pad+ma dmar po
NK014(pha)002:1750: 'dab ma brgyad pa'i lte bar nyi ma la rak+ta
NK014(pha)002:1751: am dmar por gnas pa'i ge sar es mtshan par
NK014(pha)002:1752: pa / mos la / sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)002:1753: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa go ham /
NK014(pha)002:1754: a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK014(pha)002:1755: sbyor ba'i brdas phan tshun bsnol mar bskul te /
NK014(pha)002:1756: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis 'khyud sdom sprad nas snyoms par zhugs la /
NK014(pha)002:1757: h+aum yig glur len bzhin du bskyod pas byang chub kyi sems pad+ma'i dbus su babs pa de nyid /
NK014(pha)002:1758: bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata kyis /
NK014(pha)002:1759: byang chub sems kyi rdul phra rab mkha' khyab tu
NK014(pha)002:1760: spros pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mnyes par
NK014(pha)002:1761: byas shing sems can thams cad bde ba chen pos
NK014(pha)002:1762: tshim par bsam / sam ha ra na h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:1763: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer bde ba chen po'i ro dang lhan cig par 'dus nas /
NK014(pha)002:1764: sems lnga'i mtha'i bde ba chen po'i ye shes mchog tu rgyas pa la blo bzhag ste /
NK014(pha)002:1766: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK014(pha)002:1767: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya //
NK014(pha)002:1768: mnyam pa'i grub rdzas chen po dag /
NK014(pha)002:1769: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK014(pha)002:1770: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)002:1771: zhes pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rjes
NK014(pha)002:1772: su chags pa dang dbyer med pa'i nga rgyal bya'o
NK014(pha)002:1773: // bcu gcig pa 'dod yon ro mnyam gyi mchod pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:1775: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK014(pha)002:1776: longs spyod lnga lngan thams cad ni //
NK014(pha)002:1778: chos nyid la yang chos nyid rol //
NK014(pha)002:1779: 'dod yon gyi snang ba thams cad lha dang lha mor dag pa dang /
NK014(pha)002:1780: dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad bde ba chen por
NK014(pha)002:1781: ro gcig tu gyur par bsam pa ni bla na
NK014(pha)002:1782: med pa dug gsum lam du slong ba'i mchod pa'o
NK014(pha)002:1783: // bcu gnyis pa rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:1794: rnam dag sgrib spangs srid gsum skyon bral zhing //
NK014(pha)002:1795: ston ka'i zla gsal dri med zhal mnga' ba //
NK014(pha)002:1796: bcom ldan bde gshegs thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK014(pha)002:1797: shes rab lha mo rigs kyi yum rnams dang //
NK014(pha)002:1798: phyag brnyan khro gtum rngam pa'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK014(pha)002:1799: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyi zhing rab rdzogs //
NK014(pha)002:1800: dgyes par rol cig mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK014(pha)002:1801: bzhes te a la la yis dgyes par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:1802: ces pas bdud dang log 'dren rnams tshar gcod pa dang /
NK014(pha)002:1803: mkha' khyab kyi rgyal ba dang dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo la bstod cing bskul ba dang /
NK014(pha)002:1804: chos kyi sgra rnam pa mtha' yas pa so so'i
NK014(pha)002:1805: mos pa bzhin 'char bar mos la rol mo sna
NK014(pha)002:1807: bcu gsum pa glu ye shes kyi mchod pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:1809: gtum chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK014(pha)002:1811: khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK014(pha)002:1812: mche ba zangs yag za byed che //
NK014(pha)002:1814: rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug stong ldir //
NK014(pha)002:1815: gtum chen ri rab 'bum bsnyil skad //
NK014(pha)002:1816: a la ha la'i gad rgyangs che //
NK014(pha)002:1817: spyugs pa'i 'thor rlung g.yeng ba che //
NK014(pha)002:1819: khro bo shes rab 'od po che //
NK014(pha)002:1820: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal //
NK014(pha)002:1822: sna tshogs ye shes thig le che //
NK014(pha)002:1824: khro bo'i rgyal po sprin chen po //
NK014(pha)002:1827: sna tshogs khros pa'i thig le che //
NK014(pha)002:1829: bdud kun gyi ni bdud chen po //
NK014(pha)002:1830: bdud kyi bdud de bdud rnams 'joms //
NK014(pha)002:1832: 'jigs byed chen po thig le che //
NK014(pha)002:1834: rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK014(pha)002:1835: rdo rje chu ste sdud chen po //
NK014(pha)002:1836: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che //
NK014(pha)002:1837: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che //
NK014(pha)002:1838: hoh zhes yon tan rjes su dran pa'i sgo nas bstod par bya'o //
NK014(pha)002:1839: gsum pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK014(pha)002:1843: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:1844: dzahh+aum bam hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh zhes me tog dor ba sngon du 'gro bas /
NK014(pha)002:1845: hoh spros pa med pa'i dbyings rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rnam par dag pa na /
NK014(pha)002:1846: dus gsum du gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom
NK014(pha)002:1847: ldan 'das rnam par thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK014(pha)002:1848: kyi bye brag dang ldan pa bcom ldan 'das dpal
NK014(pha)002:1849: chen po he ru ka la sogs pa rigs lnga'i
NK014(pha)002:1850: bde bar gshegs pa rigs mchog gzungs kyi yum gyii
NK014(pha)002:1851: dbyings na rnam par bzhugs pa sems dpa'i tshogs /
NK014(pha)002:1853: ye shes chen po'i dbang phyug thabs la mkhas pa'i bdag nyid sgrol ba'i mkha' 'gro /
NK014(pha)002:1858: lus pa med pa thams cad dgongs su gsol /
NK014(pha)002:1859: bdag cag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir 'tshogs pa rnams kyis /
NK014(pha)002:1860: dang po gsang ba rdo rje theg pa'i sgor khas 'ches te /
NK014(pha)002:1861: dam tshig gnyan po ma nor bar mnos pa las /
NK014(pha)002:1862: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams chag dang 'gal 'khrul du gyur pa /
NK014(pha)002:1863: lha nye bar ma bsgom pa /
NK014(pha)002:1864: snying po dag par ma bgrangs pa /
NK014(pha)002:1865: sbyor ba mang po'i bar bskums pa /
NK014(pha)002:1866: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcag pa /
NK014(pha)002:1867: dge ba can gyi thugs dkrugs pa /
NK014(pha)002:1868: mchod pa lo zla las 'das pa /
NK014(pha)002:1869: dam rdzas lag len rngo ma thogs pa /
NK014(pha)002:1872: ting nge 'dzin thang lhod du gyur pa /
NK014(pha)002:1873: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzad spyod dam pa klong du ma gyur cing /
NK014(pha)002:1874: sems can gyi spyod pa rang thad du gyur pa dang /
NK014(pha)002:1875: khyad par du sgrub pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK014(pha)002:1876: khyad par gyi dam tshig gnyan po mngon par mnos pa las /
NK014(pha)002:1877: nyams shing zhig ral du gyur pa ci mchis pa
NK014(pha)002:1878: thams cad shin tu gnong zhing 'gyod pa'i sems kyis
NK014(pha)002:1879: mthol zhing bshags par mchis na /
NK014(pha)002:1880: dbyings nyid nam mkha' dang 'dra ba'i ngang gis sku bzod pa chen po dang du bzhes nas /
NK014(pha)002:1881: tshangs pa mchog yid bzhin du thob par stsal du gsol /
NK014(pha)002:1882: zhes pa rgyud dag par byed pa 'gyod tshangs bshags pa'i rim pa'o //
NK014(pha)002:1883: bzhi pa dngos grub gsol ba ni /
NK014(pha)002:1884: shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i shes rab /
NK014(pha)002:1890: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po'i sku gsung thugs kyi bla man chad nas /
NK014(pha)002:1891: dngos grub kyi skal ba dang rigs brgyud gang lags
NK014(pha)002:1892: pa thams cad phyi mar bsdad mi 'tshal bar dus
NK014(pha)002:1893: da lta nyid du thob par stsal du gsol /
NK014(pha)002:1894: rnal 'byor pa la bar du gcod par byed pa /
NK014(pha)002:1902: so so'i rmi lam ngan pa dang /
NK014(pha)002:1904: mi shis pa'i rkyen de dag thams cad phyir bzlog
NK014(pha)002:1905: cing ming tsam yang mi grags par zhi ba chen
NK014(pha)002:1907: gal te zhi bas bsgyur du mi gtub pa zhig mchis na'ang /
NK014(pha)002:1908: drag po'i phrin las kyis dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK014(pha)002:1910: bsgral zhing spar ba la sogs te /
NK014(pha)002:1911: phrin las drag thabs rnam bzhis ji ltar 'dul bar
NK014(pha)002:1912: 'tshams pa bzhin mdzad nas ming tsam yang mi grags
NK014(pha)002:1914: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la mngon du zhugs pa rnams //
NK014(pha)002:1915: bcad gtubs sdug bsngal lus la 'byung bar mi 'gyur yang //
NK014(pha)002:1916: grib ma phog pa'i sdug bsngal shin tu mi bzod pas //
NK014(pha)002:1917: sku yi phyogs tsam mthong bas mod la 'tsho ba dang //
NK014(pha)002:1918: gzi mdangs lus la 'jug pa'i nyi ma stong phrag gi //
NK014(pha)002:1919: 'od bzhin 'jig rten khams 'dir rtag tu 'byung ba dang //
NK014(pha)002:1920: lus ngag sems la tshe 'dir rdo rje rab snang ste //
NK014(pha)002:1921: re smon thams cad dus 'di nyid du stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)002:1923: lnga pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK014(pha)002:1924: lhag pa'i bsam pa rtse gcig pas /
NK014(pha)002:1926: bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK014(pha)002:1927: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK014(pha)002:1928: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas pa //
NK014(pha)002:1929: 'gro la phan phyir bdag gis spyad //
NK014(pha)002:1930: byang chub sems mchog dam pa dang //
NK014(pha)002:1931: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK014(pha)002:1932: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong na //
NK014(pha)002:1933: rdo rje rgyal pos byin rlabs mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:1935: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' bdag gis bsgrubs //
NK014(pha)002:1936: byang chub spyod dka' bdag gis spyad //
NK014(pha)002:1938: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK014(pha)002:1942: skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba dang gsum las /
NK014(pha)002:1944: dbye gazhi'ii dkyil 'khor legs par gsal btab nas /
NK014(pha)002:1945: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he phata dzah h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram phata dzah zhes brjod pas /
NK014(pha)002:1946: dam tshig gi 'khor lo las ye shes kyi dkyil
NK014(pha)002:1947: 'khor rten dang brten par bcas pa logs su phye
NK014(pha)002:1948: nas / mdun gyi nam mkhar me ri 'dab 'byar gyi tshul du bzhugs par mos pa'o //
NK014(pha)002:1950: bdag mdun gyi lha rnams ye shes sems dapa'ii thugs
NK014(pha)002:1951: kar rdo rje'i lte bar nyi ma'i gdan sran zlum
NK014(pha)002:1952: tsam gyi dbus su rigs lnga la h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:1953: goo r+ai ma brgyad la ha /
NK014(pha)002:1956: dbang phyug ma rnams la b+h+yo re rnams ru lu
NK014(pha)002:1957: 'bru brgyad pa'i sngags kyi phreng ba re res bskor
NK014(pha)002:1960: bdag gi thugs ka nas sngags kyi 'od zer mchod pa'i tshul du spros pas /
NK014(pha)002:1961: ye shes kyi lha tshogs rnams dgyes pa bskyed /
NK014(pha)002:1963: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs dang dngos grub thams
NK014(pha)002:1964: cad 'od dang 'od zer gyi rnam pas bdag la
NK014(pha)002:1965: stsal zhing thim par dmigs pa ste /
NK014(pha)002:1966: dam ye 'phro 'du'i gsal ba gsum dang ldan pa'i ngang nas skyon bcu spangs te bzla bar bya'o //
NK014(pha)002:1968: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)002:1969: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:1971: des mtshon nas rigs bzhi dang /
NK014(pha)002:1972: gnas yul gyi ma mo sgo skyong dbang phyug ma
NK014(pha)002:1973: rnams so so'i bskyed sngags la ru lu 'bru brgyad
NK014(pha)002:1974: sbyar bas gtso 'khor gyi 'gros dang sbyar nas brgya
NK014(pha)002:1975: dang nyer gcig / bdun sogs rim par bzla zhing /
NK014(pha)002:1977: ru lu nyid la gtso bor bya'o //
NK014(pha)002:1979: rtags dus grangs kyi dbye bas rab 'bring tha ma'i tshad rdzogs kyi bar du bya bar gsungs kyang /
NK014(pha)002:1980: mos sgom nyi tshe ba la ni /
NK014(pha)002:1981: ci nus bzla ba tsam mo //
NK014(pha)002:1983: phra mo gsum gyi bzla tshul sogs ni gzhan du 'byung ba las shes par bya'o //
NK014(pha)002:1984: gsum pa skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba la /
NK014(pha)002:1987: ye shes pa bsdu ba dang gsum las /
NK014(pha)002:1989: gzhi bstod bya bar gsungs pa ltar /
NK014(pha)002:1991: dus gsum mi 'gyur rnam shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK014(pha)002:1992: zhe sdang mthar phyin badz+ra he ru ka /
NK014(pha)002:1993: dbyings nas rgyas 'debs badz+ra khros pa'i yum //
NK014(pha)002:1994: badz+ra he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)002:1995: ma 'gags rang gsal gzugs phung chos kyi sku //
NK014(pha)002:1996: gti mug mthar phyin bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK014(pha)002:1997: dbyings nas rmongs sel bud+d+ha khros pa'i yum //
NK014(pha)002:1998: bud+d+ha he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)002:1999: za byed gter tshogs tshor ba rin 'byung sku //
NK014(pha)002:2000: nga rgyal mthar phyin rat+na he ru ka /
NK014(pha)002:2001: dbyings nas tshe 'phel rat+na khros pa'i yum //
NK014(pha)002:2002: rat+na he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)002:2003: chags med dag pa 'du shes pad+ma'i sku //
NK014(pha)002:2004: 'dod chags mthar phyin pad+ma he ru ka /
NK014(pha)002:2005: dbyings nas rdzogs byed pad+ma khros pa'i yum //
NK014(pha)002:2006: pad+ma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)002:2007: don rnams mthar phyin 'du byed sprul pa'i sku //
NK014(pha)002:2008: phrag dog mthar phyin karma he ru ka /
NK014(pha)002:2009: dbyings nas za byed karma khros pa'i yum //
NK014(pha)002:2010: karma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)002:2011: 'jig rten bzhad pa'i dur khrod gnas brgyad nas //
NK014(pha)002:2012: thugs mchog rnam dag ye shes dkar mo'i tshogs //
NK014(pha)002:2013: thugs rje chen pos rnal 'byor grogs mdzad ma //
NK014(pha)002:2014: gnas kyi goo r+ai brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)002:2015: yon tan rtags kyi dur khrod gnas brgyad nas //
NK014(pha)002:2016: 'jigs byed rtsal 'phags seng gdong phra men tshogs //
NK014(pha)002:2017: thugs rje chen pos rnal 'byor grogs mdzad ma //
NK014(pha)002:2018: yul gyi phra men brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)002:2019: phyin ci log bzhi dur khrod gnas bzhi nas //
NK014(pha)002:2020: tshad med bzhi yis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:2021: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu ma //
NK014(pha)002:2022: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)002:2023: lha chen rnams kyi chung ma dbang mo'i tshogs //
NK014(pha)002:2024: 'khor ba'i chos la mnga' brnyes srin mo'i gzugs //
NK014(pha)002:2025: mya ngan 'das pa'i sprul sku mgo brnyan can //
NK014(pha)002:2026: dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)002:2027: ye shes zhi ba'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK014(pha)002:2028: gdug pa 'dul phyir 'bar ba'i skur ston pa //
NK014(pha)002:2029: khrag 'thung rol pa'i lha tshogs lnga bcu brgyad //
NK014(pha)002:2030: gdod nas ma skyes rang byung grub pa'i lha //
NK014(pha)002:2031: tshe rabs sngon nas bsgrubs pa'i 'phro mchis kyi //
NK014(pha)002:2032: da lta nyid du bdag la mngon gyur cig /
NK014(pha)002:2035: ye nas gnyis med chos skur dag pa las //
NK014(pha)002:2036: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK014(pha)002:2037: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK014(pha)002:2038: de ldog don phyir rgyal ba'i dam mnos te //
NK014(pha)002:2039: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK014(pha)002:2040: bag med tshul gyi dam las 'gal gyur pa //
NK014(pha)002:2041: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK014(pha)002:2042: thugs rje che mnga' khyod la bzod par gsol //
NK014(pha)002:2043: zhes bzlas pa'i nyes byas su gyur pa thams cad bshags par bya'o //
NK014(pha)002:2045: rang bzhin dang ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dbyer med du rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)002:2046: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:2047: zhes sogs kyis rig pa'i me tog dor ba dang dngos grub bskul ba sngar bzhin byas nas /
NK014(pha)002:2049: mdun gyi ye shes kyi 'khor lo dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor la gnyis su med par bstim la /
NK014(pha)002:2050: gsal zhing brtan pa'i phyir yi ge brgya pa'ang bazla'o //
NK014(pha)002:2051: gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga la /
NK014(pha)002:2056: spyod lam gyi rnal 'byor dang lnga /
NK014(pha)002:2057: dang po tshogs mchod la yang lnga las /
NK014(pha)002:2058: dang po bsham zhing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:2059: dza gad dang m+aam sa gtso bor gyur pa'i yo byad ci 'byor pa bshams nas /
NK014(pha)002:2061: ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ais bsang /
NK014(pha)002:2062: ram yam kham gis bsregs gtor bkrus te stong par sbyangs /
NK014(pha)002:2064: zhal zas kyi snod du nyi ma la h+aum s+w+aa
NK014(pha)002:2065: +aam h+aa las bza' btung gi dngos po ye shes
NK014(pha)002:2066: lnga'i rang bzhin bdud rtsi ro brgya pa 'dod yon
NK014(pha)002:2067: gyi rnam pa ma tshang ba med pa so so'i
NK014(pha)002:2068: lha mo'i rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang
NK014(pha)002:2069: bcas pa'i sprin 'phro bar bsam la /
NK014(pha)002:2070: yi ge gsum lan gsum brjod pas byin gyis brlab /
NK014(pha)002:2071: gnyis pa tshogs zhing spyan 'dren pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:2073: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK014(pha)002:2074: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK014(pha)002:2076: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK014(pha)002:2077: zhing chen gsar rnying stan du bting //
NK014(pha)002:2078: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK014(pha)002:2080: ma lus gshegs nas bsnams su gsol //
NK014(pha)002:2082: e h+ye hi +aa na ya dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes pas spyan drangs la dgug gzhug bcing mnyes bya /
NK014(pha)002:2083: gsum pa mchod pa la gsum las /
NK014(pha)002:2084: dang po spyir mchod pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:2086: bla med mchog gi mchod par sbyar ba 'di //
NK014(pha)002:2087: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK014(pha)002:2088: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK014(pha)002:2089: dam tshig gsang ba'i mchod par bzhes su gsol //
NK014(pha)002:2091: su ra ta u pa b+h+yah ka ma la m+aa
NK014(pha)002:2092: la badz+ra a mri ta ha ra na pra t+aits+tsha
NK014(pha)002:2093: b+ha ga w+aan / dzahh+aum bam hoh a la la hoh pa na pem pe nu su ra to /
NK014(pha)002:2095: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi hu /
NK014(pha)002:2097: sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi hu /
NK014(pha)002:2098: gnyis pa bye brag tu mchod pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:2100: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa ma //
NK014(pha)002:2102: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK014(pha)002:2105: rdo rje sgeg mo rdo rje can //
NK014(pha)002:2106: sems dpa' sngon po'i ye shes 'bebs //
NK014(pha)002:2107: me long lta bu'i ye shes las //
NK014(pha)002:2108: badz+ra l+aa s+ye'i mchod par rol //
NK014(pha)002:2109: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga l+aa s+ye h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:2112: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes las //
NK014(pha)002:2113: badz+ra m+aa le'i mchod par rol //
NK014(pha)002:2114: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga m+aa le tram /
NK014(pha)002:2115: pad+ma dbyangs mkhan rma bya'i mgrin //
NK014(pha)002:2116: spyan ras gzigs kyi dngos grub 'dzin //
NK014(pha)002:2117: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes las //
NK014(pha)002:2119: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga g+air+t+ai h+r+aih gar mkhan 'gying bag gzi ldan ma //
NK014(pha)002:2121: bya ba nan tan ye shes las //
NK014(pha)002:2123: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga n+rirti +aah zhes dang /
NK014(pha)002:2125: su ra to bcu drug gis kyang mchod do //
NK014(pha)002:2126: gsum pa khyad par gyi mchod pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:2127: tshogs phud cha gsum mam bzhir spros te /
NK014(pha)002:2130: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK014(pha)002:2131: rgod dang gshe dang 'jigs par ston pa dang //
NK014(pha)002:2132: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba la sogs pa //
NK014(pha)002:2133: sku yi dngos po shin tu bsgyur ba yin //
NK014(pha)002:2134: gar yang sgrub po rnal 'byor las //
NK014(pha)002:2135: gar gyi dbang phyug gtso bo che //
NK014(pha)002:2136: zla ba la sogs snying po can //
NK014(pha)002:2137: m+aam sa la sogs ro mchog gsol //
NK014(pha)002:2138: me tog sogs dang tsan+dana dri //
NK014(pha)002:2139: bzang rgu 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK014(pha)002:2140: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i mchog /
NK014(pha)002:2141: byin gyis rlobs shig rnal 'byor pa //
NK014(pha)002:2142: sgrub pa'i rdzas 'di thams cad la //
NK014(pha)002:2143: h+aum dang phata kyis ldan par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2144: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK014(pha)002:2150: ba lim ta pra t+aits+tsha hoh sh+r+ai m+aan kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)002:2151: zhes pas tshogs rdzas 'dod yon drug gi lha mo
NK014(pha)002:2152: mkha' khyab tu 'phros pa tshogs zhing gi lha rnams
NK014(pha)002:2153: kyi gnas drug tu thim pas dgyes par bsam mo
NK014(pha)002:2156: tshe rabs thog ma med pa tshun chad nas //
NK014(pha)002:2157: da lta'i lus 'di blangs pa yan chod du //
NK014(pha)002:2158: lus kyi sdig byas spyod pa ngan du spyad //
NK014(pha)002:2159: ngag gis tshig 'khyal smra ba ngan du brjod //
NK014(pha)002:2160: sems kyi blo nor log par bsam pa sogs //
NK014(pha)002:2161: 'dod khro gti mug dbang gis nongs bgyis pa //
NK014(pha)002:2162: bkra ba'i lha tshogs khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK014(pha)002:2163: ye shes lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK014(pha)002:2164: de yi 'khor du gtogs pa'i lha srin rnams //
NK014(pha)002:2165: mi yi skyon mthong tsam na bar chad rtsom //
NK014(pha)002:2166: nongs shing 'gal 'khrul ci bgyis mthol zhing bshags //
NK014(pha)002:2167: mthol bshags bzhes nas tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)002:2169: yi ge brgya pa yang brjod cing /
NK014(pha)002:2170: tshogs rdzas bdud rtsi lnga'i rang bzhin du phul bas
NK014(pha)002:2171: thugs dam skongs shing nyams chag dag par bsam mo
NK014(pha)002:2179: zhal du stob pa dang bdun /
NK014(pha)002:2181: ling+ga logs su bcas pa med na /
NK014(pha)002:2182: tshogs zan cha gsum pa de'i 'dod yon gyi lha
NK014(pha)002:2183: mo h+aum zhes pas rang la bsdus nas thod tshal
NK014(pha)002:2184: la sogs pa'i snod du bzhag /
NK014(pha)002:2188: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten thams cad chos kyi 'byung
NK014(pha)002:2189: gnas gru gsum mthing nag 'byams klas pa bskal pa'i
NK014(pha)002:2191: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK014(pha)002:2193: nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du bzhengs par bsam /
NK014(pha)002:2209: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:2211: lha tshogs thams cad drag po'i las la rngams shing khros par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)002:2214: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)002:2215: dkon cog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)002:2216: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)002:2217: chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)002:2218: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i
NK014(pha)002:2219: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi bden pa dang
NK014(pha)002:2220: / sprul pa yang sprul bka' sdod phyag brnyan dang bcas pa rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)002:2221: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis ma rungs
NK014(pha)002:2222: pa'i sems can bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur pa thams
NK014(pha)002:2223: cad mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la mchis par
NK014(pha)002:2224: gyur cig / n+ri yam dzah n+ri badz+ra ang+ku sha
NK014(pha)002:2225: dzah tri yam dzah tri badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah zhes
NK014(pha)002:2226: bden pa'i stobs brjod de dgug /
NK014(pha)002:2228: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata phata /
NK014(pha)002:2229: ha la ha la ha la h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:2231: sprul pa'i pho nya nam mkha' gang bar spros /
NK014(pha)002:2232: de rnams kyis gzas po skyob byed dang phral nas /
NK014(pha)002:2233: nyam thag rnam par 'gyur ba'i tshul du 'dar phril gyis bkug ste /
NK014(pha)002:2235: gzas po'i snying gi sgo phye /
NK014(pha)002:2237: zhes pas dbyer med du bstim /
NK014(pha)002:2238: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:2240: badz+ra g+han+de hoh zhes dgug bcings bsdams nas myos par bya'o //
NK014(pha)002:2242: bdag badz+ra he ru kar gsal ba'i sor mo bcu
NK014(pha)002:2243: rigs lnga yab yum du gyur pa'i sbyor mtshams nas
NK014(pha)002:2244: phur bu h+aum las badz+ra k+ai la yar bskyed pa
NK014(pha)002:2245: / sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab pa gdab cing /
NK014(pha)002:2246: e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK014(pha)002:2247: 'bar ba gtum chen rngam pa la //
NK014(pha)002:2248: khros pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK014(pha)002:2249: sangs rgyas bsod nams sku yang 'jig /
NK014(pha)002:2250: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK014(pha)002:2251: mtshan ma ming du bcas pa bya //
NK014(pha)002:2252: bkug nas rdo rje phur bus gdab //
NK014(pha)002:2253: rdul du byas nas tshogs la 'bul //
NK014(pha)002:2256: bo d+hi tsit+ta sid+d+hi ku ru h+aum h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:2257: badz+ra kro d+ha phata dzah badz+ra sat+wa h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:2261: ces gnas gsum du btab pas /
NK014(pha)002:2262: bsgral bya'i tshe dpal gzi byin thams cad h+aum zhes bdag la bstim /
NK014(pha)002:2263: gnas ngan gyi sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa sbyangs /
NK014(pha)002:2264: mi shigs pa'i thig le h+aum yig tu gyur pa bdag gi shangs bug nas drangs /
NK014(pha)002:2265: yum gyi mkha' la spros pa /
NK014(pha)002:2266: zla ba la gnas pa'i rdo rje sems dpa'i skur gyur /
NK014(pha)002:2267: de rlung gis btegs nas 'og min du 'phangs la /
NK014(pha)002:2268: snyigs ma mtshon chas dum bur gtub cing /
NK014(pha)002:2270: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK014(pha)002:2272: thal ba bzhin du brlag byas nas //
NK014(pha)002:2273: drag po'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2274: h+r+aihsh+ti bi kri t+aa na na sarba sha t+r+aum /
NK014(pha)002:2286: zhes pho'i rkang pa g.yas dang /
NK014(pha)002:2287: mo'i g.yon nas thog mar gtubs nas rim gyis bsgral zhing mtshon cha lnga'i char phab par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)002:2290: bee d+aur sngon po'i rin chen ri rab la //
NK014(pha)002:2291: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer gdal ba ltar //
NK014(pha)002:2292: sems dpa' sngon po 'od kyi dkyil 'khor can //
NK014(pha)002:2293: dpal ldan gzi byin 'bar la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)002:2294: 'od phung stug po sprin ltar 'khrigs pa yis //
NK014(pha)002:2295: 'jigs byed rngam stabs brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NK014(pha)002:2296: za byed bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar ba ste //
NK014(pha)002:2297: gdug pa thams cad rdo rje'i zhal du 'dren //
NK014(pha)002:2298: mi bzad mche ba gtsigs pa'i zhal gdangs shing //
NK014(pha)002:2299: khams gsum za bar chas pa'i rkan sgra can //
NK014(pha)002:2300: nyi zla rab tu 'bar ba'i sdang mig gis //
NK014(pha)002:2301: bdud dpung sreg par mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)002:2302: 'byung po'i sha ni zan las zhim //
NK014(pha)002:2303: gti mug mchod pa bla na med //
NK014(pha)002:2304: bla med mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)002:2305: sku yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)002:2306: 'byung po'i khrag ni chang las zhim //
NK014(pha)002:2307: 'dod chags mchod pa bla na med //
NK014(pha)002:2308: bla med mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)002:2309: gsung gi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)002:2310: 'byung po'i rus pa mar las zhim //
NK014(pha)002:2311: zhe sdang mchod pa bla na med //
NK014(pha)002:2312: bla med mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)002:2313: thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)002:2315: rtsa sngags kyi mthar kh+aa hi btags pas 'bul zhing /
NK014(pha)002:2317: tshogs rdzas dgra bgegs su dmigs nas /
NK014(pha)002:2318: bee d+aur sngon po'i bstod tshig gis phul kyang rung bar bshad do //
NK014(pha)002:2319: bzhi pa tshogs la rol ba ni /
NK014(pha)002:2320: las kyi rdo rjes 'khor lo 'dus pa'i gtso bo
NK014(pha)002:2321: la phyag byas thabs shes kyi rdzas bsnol mar 'bul
NK014(pha)002:2322: zhing / mnyam nyid mi g.yo mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas dpal //
NK014(pha)002:2323: log rtogs mtshan ma'i spros pa ngang gis zhi //
NK014(pha)002:2324: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder spyad nas kyang //
NK014(pha)002:2325: mnyam rdzogs chen po'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK014(pha)002:2327: des kyang pad+ma'i phyag rgya bskor zhing /
NK014(pha)002:2328: a la la hoh zhes len /
NK014(pha)002:2329: de nas 'dus pa gzhan rnams la yang drangs te /
NK014(pha)002:2330: rnal 'byor pa rnams lha'i rnal 'byor gsal ba las /
NK014(pha)002:2331: khyad par dkyil 'khor pa rnams rang gi phung khams
NK014(pha)002:2332: skye mched nyid las mi gnyis par shes pas nang
NK014(pha)002:2333: gi sreg blugs kyi cho ga ji lta ba'i dam
NK014(pha)002:2334: tshig gis tshim par rol lo //
NK014(pha)002:2336: hoh bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam
NK014(pha)002:2337: dral rnams kyis dza gad dpa' bo gsol bas 'gro
NK014(pha)002:2338: ba ma lus pa dbang du 'du bar gyur cig
NK014(pha)002:2339: / ma h+aa m+aam sa gsol bas rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen por gyur cig /
NK014(pha)002:2340: rdo rje'i tshe gsol bas rdo rje sems dpa'i tshe dang lang tsho la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK014(pha)002:2341: zhal zas kyi bye brag mang po gsol bas zhi
NK014(pha)002:2342: khro'i phrin las kyi rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs la dbang
NK014(pha)002:2345: lnga pa lhag ma'i cho ga la /
NK014(pha)002:2346: bsham zhing byin gyis brlab pa /
NK014(pha)002:2347: mgron 'gugs shing dbang du bya ba /
NK014(pha)002:2348: mchod pa'i las rim bstan pa /
NK014(pha)002:2351: lhag ma rnams gsog 'jog med par bsdus /
NK014(pha)002:2352: sngar zur du bcad pa'i phud dang /
NK014(pha)002:2355: mar me dang bcas pa rnams /
NK014(pha)002:2356: dkyil 'khor dang ha cang mi ring ba'i shar lhor
NK014(pha)002:2357: zhing lpags la rak+hasa chos 'byung zla gam dang bcas
NK014(pha)002:2359: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba las /
NK014(pha)002:2360: khyad par lhag ma'i gnas su /
NK014(pha)002:2361: e b+h+r+aum zhes pas lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor phyi khyams
NK014(pha)002:2362: gru gsum mthing nag 'byams klas pa'i dbus su khrag
NK014(pha)002:2363: 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gdan dang bcas pa bskyed
NK014(pha)002:2365: ngo mtshar tshogs kyi lha sum cu skad cig gis gsal bar gyur /
NK014(pha)002:2366: gtor ma zla ba gnas pa'i yig 'bar ba /
NK014(pha)002:2369: spro bsdus dam tshig gsang ba'i 'dod yon bdud rtsi'i phung po zad mi shes par bsam la /
NK014(pha)002:2373: las kyi rdo rje byed par dbang bskur ba'i //
NK014(pha)002:2374: mkha' 'gro lhag sdud ma sring ging gi tshogs //
NK014(pha)002:2375: lhag ma kha chu'i dam la gtogs pa rnams //
NK014(pha)002:2376: dam tshig bzhin du mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK014(pha)002:2378: 'dod rgyal gyi phyag rgya bcings te /
NK014(pha)002:2390: sarba badz+ra d+aa ki n+ai n+aam /
NK014(pha)002:2391: hri da yam h+aum dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh t+aa ki
NK014(pha)002:2392: h+aum dzah zhes spyugs pa'i brda dang bcas te spyan
NK014(pha)002:2393: drangs pas / lhag ma'i mgron rnams bya khyung thang
NK014(pha)002:2394: la lhags pa bzhin skad cig gis byon par bsam
NK014(pha)002:2395: drangs pas / zhing / he ru ka'i dam rgya bcings te /
NK014(pha)002:2396: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tam sa ma ya mu dra /
NK014(pha)002:2400: pad+ma ba da ba mu kha /
NK014(pha)002:2409: sarba badz+ra d+aa ki n+ai n+aam /
NK014(pha)002:2411: zhes pas phyi khyams gru gsum pa'i gdan la bzhugs par gyur /
NK014(pha)002:2412: rta gdong gi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK014(pha)002:2416: zhes dbang du bsdus pa'i ci bsgo ba'i bka' nod par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)002:2417: gsum pa mchod pa dngos la /
NK014(pha)002:2419: bye brag tu mchod pa gnyis las /
NK014(pha)002:2421: mgron rnams rigs so so'i tshom bu lngar bzhugs pas gtor ma'i bdud rtsi bzhes par bsam zhing /
NK014(pha)002:2422: he ru ka'i thod rgya bcas la /
NK014(pha)002:2423: badz+ra d+aa ki n+ai pra t+aits+tsha mam ba lim ta h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)002:2425: bud+d+ha d+aa ki n+ai sogs nas /
NK014(pha)002:2427: rat+na d+aa ki n+ai nas t+r+aam phata /
NK014(pha)002:2428: pad+ma d+aa ki n+ai nas h+r+aihphata /
NK014(pha)002:2430: ces rigs lnga phye nas mchod cing sman raka sbreng ngo //
NK014(pha)002:2431: de nas rang gi lce la rta mgrin yum bzhi
NK014(pha)002:2432: dang rol pa mdzad pa'i byang sems dza gad kyi
NK014(pha)002:2433: kha phru dang ro gcig pas mkha' dbyings kyi phyag
NK014(pha)002:2434: rgya las lhag ma dme gtor du dbab cing /
NK014(pha)002:2435: gu ru kro d+ha rat+na sa ma ya p+r+ai sha
NK014(pha)002:2436: purba bud+d+ha k+shi ta k+sho b+ha ka ra h+aum phata
NK014(pha)002:2437: / ces pas byin gyis brlabs la /
NK014(pha)002:2439: dang po phud kyis mi mchod du //
NK014(pha)002:2440: bcom ldan dpal chen phud kyi bdag /
NK014(pha)002:2441: bar du tshogs kyis mi mchod du //
NK014(pha)002:2442: ma mo mkha' 'gro tshogs kyi bdag /
NK014(pha)002:2443: tha ma lhag mas mi mchod du //
NK014(pha)002:2444: ma tshogs dbang phyug lhag ma'i gnas //
NK014(pha)002:2445: lhag ma kha chus mi gdab tu //
NK014(pha)002:2446: bran pho bran mo kha chu'i bdag /
NK014(pha)002:2447: rnam gsum rim gyis mi mchod du //
NK014(pha)002:2448: bka' dang gzhung lugs rim par yod //
NK014(pha)002:2449: rnam gsum gcig tu mi bsre ru //
NK014(pha)002:2450: chos kyi dbyings su tha mi dad //
NK014(pha)002:2451: las rnams so sor mi 'chol du //
NK014(pha)002:2452: las kyi 'du skal rim par yod //
NK014(pha)002:2453: sha khrag gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK014(pha)002:2454: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2455: ces pas dme gtor dang gtsang gtor bsres /
NK014(pha)002:2456: tshogs phud bar pa la blugs te mtshams sbyar ro //
NK014(pha)002:2457: gnyis pa bye brag tu mchod pa ni /
NK014(pha)002:2459: nam mkha' stong la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK014(pha)002:2460: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis kyang //
NK014(pha)002:2462: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK014(pha)002:2463: rnam lnga'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)002:2464: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2465: stong khams yongs la mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:2466: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyang //
NK014(pha)002:2468: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK014(pha)002:2469: rnam lnga'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)002:2470: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2471: srog dbugs kun la mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:2472: skyes bu ging chen bco brgyad kyang //
NK014(pha)002:2474: 'jig rten las kun khyed la bcol //
NK014(pha)002:2475: rnam lnga'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)002:2476: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2477: rdo rje phra men rdzu 'phrul can //
NK014(pha)002:2478: skyes bu lang+ka drug cu yang //
NK014(pha)002:2480: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK014(pha)002:2481: rnam lnga'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)002:2482: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2483: ta krita lcam mor zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:2484: 'bar ma nyul chen brgyad rnams kyang //
NK014(pha)002:2486: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK014(pha)002:2487: rnam lnga'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)002:2488: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2489: sha khrag zhal du gsol mdzad pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:2490: dur khrod dregs pa'i ma mo bdun //
NK014(pha)002:2492: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK014(pha)002:2493: rnam lnga'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)002:2494: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2495: rgyal chen sring mo zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:2496: sring mo chen mo bzhi rnams kyang //
NK014(pha)002:2498: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK014(pha)002:2499: rnam lnga'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)002:2500: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2501: phyogs bcur khyab par las byed pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:2502: pho nya sum brgya drug cu yang //
NK014(pha)002:2504: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK014(pha)002:2505: rnam lnga'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)002:2506: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2507: ri rab rmang nas 'degs mdzad pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:2508: dbang gi gru 'degs bzhi rnams kyang //
NK014(pha)002:2510: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK014(pha)002:2511: rnam lnga'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)002:2512: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2513: pha rol dmag dpung 'joms mdzad pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:2514: dmag gi rgyal mo mched bzhi yang //
NK014(pha)002:2516: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK014(pha)002:2517: rnam lnga'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)002:2518: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2520: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)002:2521: ma h+aa ba lim kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)002:2523: zhes 'bul zhing sman raka kyang sbreng /
NK014(pha)002:2526: zhes sogs kyis mchod bshags byas la /
NK014(pha)002:2527: hoh lhag sdud kyi dam tshig la gtogs pa'i mkha'
NK014(pha)002:2528: 'gro dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa
NK014(pha)002:2529: rnams lhag ma'i dam tshig 'dis tshim zhing dgyes par
NK014(pha)002:2530: gyur te / dam tshig nyams chag thams cad skongs nas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs /
NK014(pha)002:2532: dge 'dun dang chos kyi rgyal srid skyongs /
NK014(pha)002:2534: sems can gyi phan bde spel /
NK014(pha)002:2535: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi stong grogs mdzod /
NK014(pha)002:2536: sngags 'chang rnams kyi phrin las sgrubs /
NK014(pha)002:2537: khyad par du dam tshig 'dir 'dus pa rnams kyi phyi nang gsang ba'i 'gal rkyen zhi ba dang /
NK014(pha)002:2538: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa myur du 'grub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK014(pha)002:2540: ya hi gats+tsha zhes pas phyi 'khor gyi mgron rnams rang gnas su gshegs par bsam la /
NK014(pha)002:2542: h+aum zhes pas lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha sum
NK014(pha)002:2543: cu rang gi snying gar bsdus la man+dala yang bsdu'o
NK014(pha)002:2544: // de tsam mi nus pas lhag gtor shin tu bsdus pa la dga' na /
NK014(pha)002:2545: mgron bkug nas lhag ma kha chus bran te phud lhag bsres la /
NK014(pha)002:2546: rigs lnga'i gtor sngags kyis mchod pa'i rjes su /
NK014(pha)002:2547: rgyud kyi le'u nyi shu par 'byung ba'i dam bsgrag
NK014(pha)002:2548: cing las bcol ba tsam btags kyang rung bar mngon
NK014(pha)002:2549: no // gnyis pa brtan ma bskyang ba ni /
NK014(pha)002:2550: phyi rol du brtan ma'i gtor ma sman phud kyis bran la /
NK014(pha)002:2555: gtor ma'i rdul phra rab re re zhing rin po
NK014(pha)002:2556: che'i gur khang longs spyod zad mi shes pas nam
NK014(pha)002:2560: tshogs dang bka' yi tshogs bcas nyid //
NK014(pha)002:2561: khrag 'thung de bzhin nam mkha'i sku //
NK014(pha)002:2562: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs skyong ma rnams //
NK014(pha)002:2563: 'dir spyon dam skongs phrin las mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2564: bdag nyid chen mo la sogs bdud mo bzhi //
NK014(pha)002:2565: gangs dkar sha med la sogs gnod sbyin bzhi //
NK014(pha)002:2566: kong btsun de mo la sogs sman mo bzhi //
NK014(pha)002:2567: bod khams skyong ba'i che zhe chen mo rnams //
NK014(pha)002:2568: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas //
NK014(pha)002:2569: lhab lhub mang po'i rgyan dang bcas //
NK014(pha)002:2570: sil snyan mang po'i sgra dang bcas //
NK014(pha)002:2571: 'dir spyon dam skongs phrin las mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2572: che zhe chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK014(pha)002:2573: a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK014(pha)002:2575: rlangs chen dpal gyi seng ge yis //
NK014(pha)002:2576: zhing chen stan la bkod nas kyang //
NK014(pha)002:2577: lag tu rdo rje gtad nas ni //
NK014(pha)002:2578: dbang bskur gsang ba'i mtshan nas brjod //
NK014(pha)002:2579: rdo rje 'chang gi gral du bzhag /
NK014(pha)002:2580: bod khams bsrung zhing skyong ba dang //
NK014(pha)002:2581: rnal 'byor sgrub pa'i grogs bya zhes //
NK014(pha)002:2582: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:2583: g.yar dam gnyan po rjes dgongs la //
NK014(pha)002:2584: dam rdzas bka' yi gtor ma longs //
NK014(pha)002:2585: bcol ba'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2591: ma ma sring 'gro ma h+aum b+h+yo h+aum h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:2593: ma h+aa pany+tsa sogs kyis sman gtor rak+tasa kyang mchod cing sman raka sbreng /
NK014(pha)002:2595: ya hi gats+tshasa gshegs gsol byas la /
NK014(pha)002:2596: gtor ma gtsang sar skyel lo //
NK014(pha)002:2597: gsum pa nyer bsdu bya ba ni /
NK014(pha)002:2598: thun mtshams la 'jug pa'am nyal ba na /
NK014(pha)002:2601: zhes pas dkyil 'khor gsal btab la /
NK014(pha)002:2602: skabs 'dir mchod bstod dang bzod gsol ni byas kyang rung ma byas kyang mi 'gal lo //
NK014(pha)002:2603: de nas rtag mtha' bsal phyir /
NK014(pha)002:2606: rang gi snying ga'i 'od kyis phog pas dag pa'i snod bcud thams cad gzhal yas khang la thim /
NK014(pha)002:2607: gzhal yas khang gi rgyan thams cad yab rnams la thim /
NK014(pha)002:2608: dngos po thams cad yum rnams la /
NK014(pha)002:2609: 'khor rnams phyi nas rim bzhin gtso bo yab yum la /
NK014(pha)002:2611: de ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK014(pha)002:2614: h+aum gyen rdzogs n+aa da'i bar du bsdus nas mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su bstim mo //
NK014(pha)002:2616: nyal ba las langs pa'am spyod lam la 'jug pa na /
NK014(pha)002:2617: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK014(pha)002:2619: dpal chen po he ru ka zhal gcig phyag gnyis
NK014(pha)002:2620: pa snang stong sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i skur ldang ngo
NK014(pha)002:2621: // bzhi pa go cha bgo zhing lus bsrung ba ni /
NK014(pha)002:2624: snying gar h+aum yig rnams kyis mtshan par bsam zhing /
NK014(pha)002:2625: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha ham /
NK014(pha)002:2627: lus thams cad rdo rje'i go chas bcings te cis kyang mi shigs par bltas la /
NK014(pha)002:2628: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK014(pha)002:2629: sku gsung thugs kyis kun la khyab //
NK014(pha)002:2630: ces brjod cing nga rgyal bya /
NK014(pha)002:2631: de nas mdzub mo g.yas g.yon gnyis dang trum las
NK014(pha)002:2632: rdo rje gnod sbyin dang mi 'chi thabs sbyor bskyed
NK014(pha)002:2633: la / lte ba snying ga ltag pa dang //
NK014(pha)002:2634: dpral ba spyi bo gnas lnga ru //
NK014(pha)002:2636: zhes brjod bzhin par mdzub mo gnyis bsnol te rim par reg pas /
NK014(pha)002:2637: khro bo gnyis dang rdo rje'i lu gu rgyud kyis bsrung zhing brtan par bya'o //
NK014(pha)002:2638: de nas thod pa'i phyag rgya mgo bo'i gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK014(pha)002:2639: badz+ra ka p+aa la a b+hi shiny+tsa tram tram /
NK014(pha)002:2640: zhes thod pa'i khang bu rigs lnga'i cod pan can gyis dbang bskur bar mos /
NK014(pha)002:2641: dar dpyangs kyi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK014(pha)002:2642: +aar+ya lam+b+ho d+har a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aihh+r+aih zhes pas cod pan mthing ga g.yas su 'phyang zhing /
NK014(pha)002:2643: dmar mo g.yon du 'phur bar bsam mo //
NK014(pha)002:2644: gu h+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)002:2646: yi ge brgya pa lan gsum la sogs par bzlas pas shin tu brtan par byas la /
NK014(pha)002:2647: dge ba bsngo zhing bkra shis brjod pa rnams kyiis mtha' rgyas par bya'o //
NK014(pha)002:2648: lnga pa spyod lam rgyun gyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK014(pha)002:2649: de ltar dkyil 'khor bsdus nas kyang //
NK014(pha)002:2650: rnal 'byor bdag nyid chen po yis //
NK014(pha)002:2651: spyod lam kun tu mi nyams par //
NK014(pha)002:2652: lha nyid du ni rtag tu bsgom //
NK014(pha)002:2653: zhes gsungs pas snod thams cad gzhal yas khang dang /
NK014(pha)002:2654: bcud thams cad he ru ka'i rang bzhin du shes pas spyod lam bskyang ngo //
NK014(pha)002:2656: dbu ma'i nang du mi rtog pa'i thig le me
NK014(pha)002:2657: stag phus btab pa lta bu yungs 'bru tsam zhig
NK014(pha)002:2659: sngar bshad pa'i nyer bsdu'i mtha'i h+aum gi n+aa da
NK014(pha)002:2660: shin tu phra ba la shes pa gtod pa ste
NK014(pha)002:2661: / dub na ye shes thig le blta //
NK014(pha)002:2664: nang gi sbyin sreg blang bar bya //
NK014(pha)002:2665: zhes pas bza' btung la tha mal gyi gtsang zhen
NK014(pha)002:2666: spangs nas sbyang rtogs sbar bas bdud rtsir byas pa
NK014(pha)002:2667: lag pa'i dgang blugs kyis kha'i thab khung du phul
NK014(pha)002:2668: ba gtum mo'i mes bzhu ba'i dwangs mas snying ga'i
NK014(pha)002:2669: ye shes sems dpa' mchod par bsam la rol pa
NK014(pha)002:2670: ni nang gi sbyin sreg go //
NK014(pha)002:2671: spyi don gsum pa grub pa 'bras bu'i tshul la /
NK014(pha)002:2673: des grub pa'i tshad bstan pa'o //
NK014(pha)002:2675: gang gis glang chen myos 'dra'i sems //
NK014(pha)002:2676: mnyam par bzhag pas btul nas su //
NK014(pha)002:2677: sngags dang phyag rgya rab brtan na //
NK014(pha)002:2678: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'gyur //
NK014(pha)002:2679: zhes pas mnyam rjes kun tu lta ba 'khor 'das mnyam nyid du shes pa dang /
NK014(pha)002:2680: spyod pa rtsal snang dag pa rab 'byams su rgyas
NK014(pha)002:2681: 'debs kyi rnal 'byor dang mi 'bral ba la bslab
NK014(pha)002:2683: de ltar nges rdzogs su bslabs pas phyag rgya gcig
NK014(pha)002:2684: pa dang spros bcas la nyams lnga mthar phyin nas
NK014(pha)002:2685: thun mong gi dngos grub dang /
NK014(pha)002:2687: yan lag ma nyams yo byad ldan //
NK014(pha)002:2688: cho ga rdzogs par shes pa yis //
NK014(pha)002:2690: nges par legs pa'i dgos pa 'grub //
NK014(pha)002:2691: khro bo khro mo'i tshogs chen po //
NK014(pha)002:2692: pho nya phyag brnyan bka' nyan sogs //
NK014(pha)002:2693: ci bgyi la sogs tshogs rnams kyis //
NK014(pha)002:2694: dngos grub las rnams rdzogs par byed //
NK014(pha)002:2695: ces gsungs pa ltar tshogs sgrub kyi nye rgyu la
NK014(pha)002:2696: brten nas bsgrubs pas dbang po rno na tshe dbang
NK014(pha)002:2697: rig 'dzin dang / rtul na'ang rnam smin rig 'dzin zla ba drug las mi 'gyangs par 'thob la /
NK014(pha)002:2698: de nas lhag bcas lhag med gang rung gis phyag
NK014(pha)002:2699: chen dang lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi sa bgrod nas
NK014(pha)002:2700: dpal he ru ka'i go 'phang la gnas par 'gyur
NK014(pha)002:2701: ro // de la thun mong gi dngos grub gang zhe na /
NK014(pha)002:2703: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel zhing //
NK014(pha)002:2704: longs spyod 'byung zhing ngan song sbyong //
NK014(pha)002:2705: ci yang gzhan du gyur ba 'grub //
NK014(pha)002:2706: ces pas yon tan 'byung ba'i dngos grub drug dang /
NK014(pha)002:2707: nam mkha' rdo rje sra 'byung zhing //
NK014(pha)002:2711: thams cad stong zhing ltung bar 'gyur //
NK014(pha)002:2712: zhes pas 'byung ba'i dngos grub lnga dang /
NK014(pha)002:2713: dgug dang btang dang bcing dang dgrol //
NK014(pha)002:2714: gso dang bsad dang pham dang rgyal //
NK014(pha)002:2716: zhes pas las phran tshegs kyi dngos grub brgyad de /
NK014(pha)002:2717: bshad rgyud las ni gzhan yang mang du gsungs so //
NK014(pha)002:2718: mchog gi dngos grub gang zhe na //
NK014(pha)002:2719: dus gsum rgyal bas thugs chud pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:2720: dngos grub mchog gi snying po ni //
NK014(pha)002:2721: zad pa'i dus med yid bzhin mdzod //
NK014(pha)002:2724: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba che //
NK014(pha)002:2725: 'gyur med bde chen snying po yid bzhin nor //
NK014(pha)002:2726: rgyud don dpag daka'i rgya mtsho cher sbas pa //
NK014(pha)002:2727: dus mtha'i sngags pas phyogs mthong tsam yang dkon //
NK014(pha)002:2728: la la rnyed bkur 'ching bu don gnyer blos //
NK014(pha)002:2729: zab mo'i gting mtha' ma dpyad gya tshoms su //
NK014(pha)002:2730: zhugs pas tshig 'khrul mu cor sgrog bzhin pas //
NK014(pha)002:2731: don nor rlabs phreng mjing du lhungs pa mthong //
NK014(pha)002:2732: de phyir zab rgyas rgya mtshor bder 'jug pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:2733: spobs pa bral yang dam pa'i ded dpon dang //
NK014(pha)002:2734: dri med gzhung lugs mthong brgyud gru skya la //
NK014(pha)002:2735: brten nas snying stobs gzings kyi 'phrul 'khor bshams //
NK014(pha)002:2736: srid gsum nyon mongs gdung sel yid bzhin nor //
NK014(pha)002:2737: bde chen char du 'bebs pa 'dod 'jo'i sprin //
NK014(pha)002:2738: phrin las rgyal mtshan rtse mor mchod rlom gyi //
NK014(pha)002:2739: 'dod pa'i re skong mdzod cig he ru kah gang gi sgrub thabs rim pa dang po'i khrigs //
NK014(pha)002:2740: blo dman rnams kyis bde blag rtogs bya'i phyir //
NK014(pha)002:2741: gsal bar bkod mod nongs gang bla ma lha //
NK014(pha)002:2742: chos spyan mnga' ba bcas la bzod par gsol //
NK014(pha)002:2743: phyogs lhung dri mar zhen pa 'khyog po'i blo //
NK014(pha)002:2744: legs bshad bskal brgyar bsnyad kyang mi mgu bas //
NK014(pha)002:2745: de dag 'bad pas dmod kyang skyon yod min //
NK014(pha)002:2746: rnam dpyod drang po'i blo can rnams la gsal //
NK014(pha)002:2747: 'di las bsod nams phung po gang thob pa'i //
NK014(pha)002:2748: dge legs bstan 'gro'i phan bde rab 'byams kyi //
NK014(pha)002:2749: nyer 'tshor gyur nas bdag kyang srid mtha'i bar //
NK014(pha)002:2750: rgyal ba kun gyi gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin shog /
NK014(pha)002:2751: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo he ru ka'i dkyil
NK014(pha)002:2752: 'khor bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs bde chen char 'bebs zhes
NK014(pha)002:2753: bya ba 'di ni rang gzhan mang po la phan
NK014(pha)002:2754: pa'i bsam pas / 'di nyid kyi rgyud dang rgya gzhung rnams dang /
NK014(pha)002:2755: de dag gi bshad srol 'khrul med brgyud pa'i phyag bzhes su ji ltar mdzad pa'i gzhung bzung ste /
NK014(pha)002:2756: gsang bdag chen po phrin las lhun grub kyi gsung
NK014(pha)002:2757: gi 'od zer gyi blo'i pad+mo rnam par bzhad pa
NK014(pha)002:2758: sh+aakya'i dge bsnyen rig pa 'dzin pa 'gyur med rdo
NK014(pha)002:2759: rjes ing+ge ra'i lo s+n+ron gyi zla ba tshes pa
NK014(pha)002:2760: la o rgyan smin grol gling nges pa don gyi
NK014(pha)002:2761: dga' ba'i tshal chen po'i gtsug lag khang du sbyar
NK014(pha)002:2762: ba'i yi ge pa ni rgyud sde 'di nyid kyi
NK014(pha)002:2763: tshig don smra ba la thogs pa med pa'i blo
NK014(pha)002:2764: gros kyi mthu grub pa mkhan chen lo ts+aa ba
NK014(pha)002:2766: 'dis kyang rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che phyogs
NK014(pha)002:2767: thams cad du dar zhing rgyas la yun ring du
